#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:137
msgid ""
"Perry's codegen translates the user's TS-side calls "
"(`mysql.createConnection(config)`, `c.query(sql, params)`) into direct calls"
" to these symbols, with the right argument coercion (JsValue NaN-box ↔ f64 "
"ABI shim, string-pointer extraction, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Perry 的代码生成会把用户 TS 端的调用(`mysql.createConnection(config)`、`c.query(sql, "
"params)`)翻译为对这些符号的直接调用,并完成正确的参数转换(JsValue NaN-box ↔ f64 ABI 适配、字符串指针提取等)。"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:142
msgid ""
"Those manifest entries are native ABI descriptors, not TypeScript types. A "
"descriptor like `f32` or `usize` chooses the native slot used for the C call"
" and still appears to user code as a JavaScript `number`; `buffer+len` "
"consumes one Buffer/Uint8Array-shaped argument and emits `(ptr, usize)` "
"native slots; `handle<T>` and `promise<T>` carry metadata while remaining "
"opaque runtime handles at the boundary. See "
"[`manifest-v1.md`](manifest-v1.md) for the full descriptor vocabulary and "
"the legacy string aliases that remain accepted."
msgstr ""
"这些 manifest 条目是原生 ABI 描述符，而非 TypeScript 类型。像 `f32` 或 `usize` 这样的描述符决定了 C "
"调用所使用的原生插槽，在用户代码中仍然表现为 JavaScript 的 `number`；`buffer+len` 消费一个 "
"Buffer/Uint8Array 形式的参数，并生成 `(ptr, usize)` 原生插槽；`handle<T>` 和 `promise<T>` "
"携带元数据，但在边界处仍为不透明的运行时句柄。完整的描述符词汇表及仍被接受的旧版字符串别名，请参阅 "
"[`manifest-v1.md`](manifest-v1.md)。"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:151
msgid "4. Linking"
msgstr "4. 链接"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:153
msgid ""
"The staticlib (`libperry_ext_mysql2.a` for the well-known case, or a "
"prebuilt artifact in `node_modules/mysql2/prebuilt/<target>/` for the "
"external case) joins the link line alongside `libperry_runtime.a` and "
"`libperry_stdlib.a`. The `js_mysql2_*` symbol references in the user's "
"compiled code resolve at link time."
msgstr ""
"静态库(已知情形下为 `libperry_ext_mysql2.a`,外部情形下为 "
"`node_modules/mysql2/prebuilt/<target>/` 中的预构建产物)与 "
"`libperry_runtime.a`、`libperry_stdlib.a` 一起加入链接行。用户编译代码中对 `js_mysql2_*` "
"符号的引用在链接时被解析。"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:159
msgid ""
"If the binding ships only Rust source (no prebuilt), Perry runs `cargo build"
" --release` on the wrapper at compile time. Slow first build, then cached."
msgstr ""
"如果绑定只发布 Rust 源码(无预构建),Perry 会在编译时对 wrapper 运行 `cargo build "
"--release`。首次构建较慢,之后会被缓存。"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:163
msgid "5. Runtime"
msgstr "5. 运行时"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:165
msgid ""
"User code runs. Calls into `js_mysql2_*` happen at native speed — function "
"call overhead is one register-pass for the receiver handle plus one each per"
" param. Promise resolution / closure invocation / async work bridge through "
"perry-ffi's surface (`JsPromise`, `JsClosure`, `spawn_blocking + "
"tokio::Handle::current().block_on`). The wrapper sees Perry's NaN-boxed "
"JsValues directly; user TypeScript sees a normal Promise / object / array."
msgstr ""
"用户代码运行。对 `js_mysql2_*` 的调用以原生速度发生——函数调用开销是接收者句柄一次寄存器传递,加上每个参数一次。Promise 解决 /"
" 闭包调用 / 异步工作通过 perry-ffi 的接口(`JsPromise`、`JsClosure`、`spawn_blocking + "
"tokio::Handle::current().block_on`)进行桥接。wrapper 直接看到 Perry 的 NaN-boxed "
"JsValue;用户 TypeScript 看到的是普通的 Promise / 对象 / 数组。"

