"\"C\"` export plus the build config. Schema details in "
"[`manifest-v1.md`](manifest-v1.md)."
msgstr ""
"`perry.nativeLibrary` 块用于告知 Perry 编译器每一个 `extern \"C\"` 导出以及构建配置。完整 schema "
"详见 [`manifest-v1.md`](manifest-v1.md)。"

