#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:1
msgid "`perry-ffi` — the stable ABI for native bindings"
msgstr "`perry-ffi` —— 原生绑定的稳定 ABI"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:3
msgid ""
"This page documents the contract between native bindings packages "
"(`perryts/mysql2-bindings`, `@perry/iroh`, `perry-ext-dotenv`, …) and the "
"Perry runtime they execute inside."
msgstr ""
"本页文档化了原生绑定包（`perryts/mysql2-bindings`、`@perry/iroh`、`perry-ext-dotenv` "
"等）与它们运行其中的 Perry 运行时之间的契约。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:7
msgid ""
"**New here?** Start with [Native Bindings — Overview](overview.md) for the "
"architectural picture and the [Authoring Guide](authoring-guide.md) for the "
"step-by-step. This page is reference-grade detail."
msgstr ""
"**初次接触？** 请先阅读 [Native Bindings — Overview](overview.md) 了解整体架构图景，再阅读 "
"[Authoring Guide](authoring-guide.md) 获取分步指南。本页是参考级细节。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:12
msgid ""
"It is intentionally short. The whole point of the contract is _minimum "
"surface area_ — every helper added is a forever commitment, and Perry's "
"internals (string layout, NaN-boxing tags, GC) are free to change underneath"
" as long as this surface holds."
msgstr ""
"本页有意保持简短。整个契约的核心就是 _最小表面积_ —— 每个 helper 都是永久承诺，而 Perry 的内部实现（字符串布局、NaN "
"装箱标签、GC）只要不破坏此表面就可以自由演进。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:17 src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:24
msgid "Versioning"
msgstr "版本管理"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:19
msgid ""
"`perry-ffi` ships its own semver, currently tracking Perry's minor: `perry-"
"ffi = \"0.5\"` for Perry `0.5.x`."
msgstr ""
"`perry-ffi` 拥有自己的 semver，目前与 Perry 的 minor 同步：Perry `0.5.x` 对应 `perry-ffi = "
"\"0.5\"`。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:22
msgid ""
"**v0.5.x consumption (current)**: until the v0.6.0 type-source-of-truth "
"refactor lands, `perry-ffi` re-exports a handful of types from `perry-"
"runtime` (`StringHeader`, `ArrayHeader`, `ObjectHeader`, `BigIntHeader`, "
"`BufferHeader`, `ClosureHeader`, `Promise`). That makes it un-publishable to"
" crates.io as-is — `perry-runtime` is a private dep and not something we "
"want on crates.io. Wrappers depend on `perry-ffi` via the git URL while "
"we're in the v0.5.x cycle:"
msgstr ""
"**v0.5.x 的引用方式（当前）**：在 v0.6.0 类型来源重构落地之前，`perry-ffi` 会从 `perry-runtime` "
"重新导出少量类型（`StringHeader`、`ArrayHeader`、`ObjectHeader`、`BigIntHeader`、`BufferHeader`、`ClosureHeader`、`Promise`）。这使其在当前形态下无法发布到"
" crates.io —— `perry-runtime` 是私有依赖，我们也不希望把它放到 crates.io。在 v0.5.x 周期内，封装通过 "
"git URL 依赖 `perry-ffi`："

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:36
msgid ""
"`PerryTS/tursodb-bindings` and `PerryTS/iroh-bindings` ship this shape and "
"`cargo build` against the live `main` branch."
msgstr ""
"`PerryTS/tursodb-bindings` 和 `PerryTS/iroh-bindings` 都采用这种形态，并对实时的 `main` "
"分支执行 `cargo build`。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:39
msgid ""
"**v0.6.0 plan (deferred)**: invert the type ownership so `perry-ffi` becomes"
" the source of truth — it defines `#[repr(C)]` versions of the ABI types "
"itself, exposes opaque pointers for `Promise` / `ClosureHeader` (which have "
"private state), and `perry-runtime` imports the types from `perry-ffi`. At "
"that point `perry-ffi` has zero `perry-runtime` deps and can publish to "
"crates.io as `perry-ffi = \"0.6\"` — wrappers switch to `cargo add perry-"
"ffi`. Tracked under [\\#466 Phase "
"1](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/466) as a v0.6.0 followup; the "
"v0.5.x git-URL approach is supported and tested end-to-end in the meantime."
msgstr ""
"**v0.6.0 计划（已推迟）**：反转类型归属，使 `perry-ffi` 成为唯一权威 —— 它自己定义 ABI 类型的 `#[repr(C)]`"
" 版本，对具有私有状态的 `Promise` / `ClosureHeader` 暴露不透明指针，由 `perry-runtime` 从 `perry-"
"ffi` 导入这些类型。届时 `perry-ffi` 将不再依赖 `perry-runtime`，可以作为 `perry-ffi = \"0.6\"` "
"发布到 crates.io —— 封装可以切换为 `cargo add perry-ffi`。该工作在 [\\#466 Phase "
"1](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/466) 中跟踪，作为 v0.6.0 "
"后续工作；在此期间，v0.5.x 的 git URL 方案是受支持并经过端到端测试的。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:49
msgid "A wrapper's `package.json` declares the ABI it was built against:"
msgstr "封装的 `package.json` 会声明它针对的 ABI："

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:56 src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:34
#: src/cli/allow-perry-features.md:54
msgid "\"...\""
msgstr "\"...\""

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:62
msgid ""
"The Perry compiler refuses to load a wrapper whose declared `abiVersion` "
"doesn't satisfy the bundled `perry-ffi`'s semver range (strict enforcement "
"lands under issue [\\#466 Phase "
"2](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/466)). Backwards- incompatible "
"changes to anything in this document bump perry-ffi's _major_ version — "
"independent of `perry-runtime` semver."
msgstr ""
"如果封装声明的 `abiVersion` 不满足捆绑的 `perry-ffi` 的 semver 范围，Perry 编译器会拒绝加载它（严格校验在 "
"issue [\\#466 Phase 2](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/466) "
"中落地）。本文档中任何向后不兼容的变更都会提升 perry-ffi 的 _主_ 版本号 —— 这与 `perry-runtime` 的 semver "
"相互独立。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:68
msgid "Surface (v0.5.x)"
msgstr "表面（v0.5.x）"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:70
msgid ""
"The current surface is _deliberately minimal_ — just enough to port the "
"simplest stdlib wrappers (`dotenv`, `nanoid`, `uuid`, `slugify`). It will "
"grow as real wrappers demand it; we'd rather under-design and add than "
"commit to a helper we later regret."
msgstr ""
"当前表面 _刻意精简_ —— 只够移植最简单的 stdlib "
"封装（`dotenv`、`nanoid`、`uuid`、`slugify`）。它会随真实封装的需求增长；我们宁愿先少设计后再添加，也不愿承诺一个日后会后悔的"
" helper。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:78
msgid "/* opaque */"
msgstr "/* opaque */"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:89
msgid "// for `*mut StringHeader` in extern \"C\" sigs\n"
msgstr "// for `*mut StringHeader` in extern \"C\" sigs\n"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:92
msgid ""
"`alloc_string` allocates a fresh string in the runtime's arena. The handle "
"is owned by the runtime — Perry's GC reclaims it once no live references "
"remain, including references held by JS code your function returned the "
"handle to."
msgstr ""
"`alloc_string` 在运行时的 arena 中分配一个新字符串。该 handle 由运行时拥有 —— 一旦没有任何活跃引用（包括你将 "
"handle 返回给 JS 代码后由其持有的引用），Perry 的 GC 会回收它。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:97
msgid ""
"`read_string` borrows the underlying UTF-8 bytes for the duration of the FFI"
" call. Returns `None` on a null handle or invalid UTF-8."
msgstr ""
"`read_string` 在 FFI 调用期间借用底层的 UTF-8 字节。当 handle 为 null 或字节非合法 UTF-8 时返回 "
"`None`。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:100
msgid ""
"`StringHeader` is re-exported as the canonical type for `extern \"C\"` "
"return / parameter types — wrappers should write `pub extern \"C\" fn "
"js_my_module_thing() -> *mut perry_ffi::StringHeader`, not import "
"`StringHeader` from `perry-runtime` directly."
msgstr ""
"`StringHeader` 作为 `extern \"C\"` 返回值 / 参数类型的规范类型重新导出 —— 封装应当写成 `pub extern "
"\"C\" fn js_my_module_thing() -> *mut perry_ffi::StringHeader`，而不要直接从 "
"`perry-runtime` 导入 `StringHeader`。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:105
msgid "What's NOT in v0.5"
msgstr "v0.5 中尚未提供的内容"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:107
msgid ""
"These will land as real wrappers force them, tracked under [\\#466 Phase "
"1](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/466)'s \"Open questions\":"
msgstr ""
"随着真实封装提出需求，这些将逐步落地，跟踪在 [\\#466 Phase "
"1](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/466) 的“Open questions”下："

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:110
msgid "Array allocation / read (`alloc_array`, `read_array`)."
msgstr "数组分配 / 读取（`alloc_array`、`read_array`）。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:111
msgid "Object field get / set."
msgstr "对象字段 get / set。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:112
msgid "Closure invocation helpers."
msgstr "闭包调用辅助函数。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:113
msgid "NaN-boxing constants (undefined / null / true / false)."
msgstr "NaN 装箱常量（undefined / null / true / false）。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:114
msgid "Async runtime sharing (`spawn_async`, `block_on`)."
msgstr "异步运行时共享（`spawn_async`、`block_on`）。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:115
msgid "BigInt allocation."
msgstr "BigInt 分配。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:117
msgid ""
"If your wrapper needs one of these today, add it to perry-ffi in the same PR"
" that ports the wrapper. Treat this document as the review gate: any "
"addition needs a one-line entry above and a unit test in `crates/perry-"
"ffi/src/lib.rs`."
msgstr ""
"如果你的封装现在就需要其中之一，请在移植该封装的同一个 PR 中将其加入 perry-"
"ffi。把本文档当作评审关卡：任何新增都需要在上文增加一行条目，并在 `crates/perry-ffi/src/lib.rs` 中添加单元测试。"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:122
msgid "Reference example: `perry-ext-dotenv`"
msgstr "参考示例：`perry-ext-dotenv`"

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:124
