#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:1
msgid "`perry.nativeLibrary` manifest — spec v1"
msgstr "`perry.nativeLibrary` manifest —— 规范 v1"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:3
msgid ""
"**New here?** Start with [Native Bindings — Overview](overview.md) for the "
"architectural picture and the [Authoring Guide](authoring-guide.md) for a "
"step-by-step that uses this manifest. This page is reference-grade detail."
msgstr ""
"**初次接触？** 请先阅读 [Native Bindings — Overview](overview.md) 了解整体架构图景，再阅读使用本 "
"manifest 的 [Authoring Guide](authoring-guide.md) 获取分步指南。本页是参考级细节。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:8
msgid ""
"This page is the authoritative spec for the `perry.nativeLibrary` field a "
"native-bindings package declares in its `package.json`. The Perry compiler "
"reads this manifest at resolve time and uses it to:"
msgstr ""
"本页是原生绑定包在其 `package.json` 中声明的 `perry.nativeLibrary` 字段的权威规范。Perry "
"编译器会在解析期读取该 manifest 并据此："

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:12
msgid ""
"Decide whether the import is \"native\" (calls into a Rust `staticlib`) vs. "
"plain TypeScript / JavaScript."
msgstr "判断该导入是“原生”（调用 Rust `staticlib`）还是普通 TypeScript / JavaScript。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:14
msgid ""
"Map TypeScript-side function calls onto the right `extern \"C\"` symbol with"
" the right calling convention."
msgstr "将 TypeScript 端的函数调用以正确的调用约定映射到对应的 `extern \"C\"` 符号。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:16
msgid ""
"Pull the right `.a` archive into the link line, with the right frameworks / "
"system libs / pkg-config dependencies for the user's compile target."
msgstr "为用户的编译目标，将正确的 `.a` 归档以及正确的 frameworks / 系统库 / pkg-config 依赖纳入链接命令。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:20
msgid ""
"A companion JSON schema lives at "
"[`docs/api/manifest.schema.json`](../../api/manifest.schema.json) for editor"
" validation."
msgstr ""
"配套的 JSON schema 位于 "
"[`docs/api/manifest.schema.json`](../../api/manifest.schema.json)，可用于编辑器校验。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:26
msgid ""
"The schema is versioned via the `abiVersion` field. Every wrapper declares "
"which `perry-ffi` ABI it was built against:"
msgstr "schema 通过 `abiVersion` 字段进行版本管理。每个封装都声明其针对的 `perry-ffi` ABI："

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:40
msgid ""
"The `perry` binary refuses to load a wrapper whose declared `abiVersion` "
"doesn't satisfy the bundled `perry-ffi`'s semver range."
msgstr ""
"如果封装声明的 `abiVersion` 不满足捆绑的 `perry-ffi` 的 semver 范围，`perry` 二进制将拒绝加载该封装。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:43
msgid ""
"**Transitional rule for the v0.5.x cycle**: missing `abiVersion` is allowed "
"but emits a warning naming the package and pointing at this spec. From "
"v0.6.0 onwards it becomes a hard error."
msgstr ""
"**v0.5.x 周期的过渡规则**：允许缺少 `abiVersion`，但会发出警告，指明包名并指向本规范。从 v0.6.0 开始这将成为硬性错误。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:47
msgid ""
"See [`docs/src/native-libraries/abi.md`](abi.md) for what the v0.5 ABI "
"surface actually contains."
msgstr "v0.5 ABI 表面实际包含哪些内容，请参阅 [`docs/src/native-libraries/abi.md`](abi.md)。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:50
msgid "Top-level shape"
msgstr "顶层结构"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:52
msgid ""
"```jsonc\n"
"{\n"
"  \"perry\": {\n"
"    \"nativeLibrary\": {\n"
"      // Required from v0.6.0; warning-only in v0.5.x.\n"
"      \"abiVersion\": \"0.5\",\n"
"\n"
"      // FFI function declarations — what TypeScript-side\n"
"      // call sites bind to. See \"Functions\" below.\n"
"      \"functions\": [\n"
"        { \"name\": \"js_my_thing\", \"params\": [\"string\"], \"returns\": \"string\" }\n"
"      ],\n"
"\n"
"      // Per-target build configuration. Optional; if omitted, no\n"
"      // crate is built and the wrapper is purely a `.d.ts`-style\n"
"      // declaration of pre-built symbols (rare).\n"
"      \"targets\": {\n"
"        \"macos\":     { \"...\": \"...\" },\n"
"        \"ios\":       { \"...\": \"...\" },\n"
"        \"linux\":     { \"...\": \"...\" },\n"
"        \"windows\":   { \"...\": \"...\" },\n"
"        \"android\":   { \"...\": \"...\" },\n"
"        \"web\":       { \"...\": \"...\" },\n"
"        \"harmonyos\": { \"...\": \"...\" },\n"
"        \"tvos\":      { \"...\": \"...\" },\n"
"        \"watchos\":   { \"...\": \"...\" },\n"
"        \"visionos\":  { \"...\": \"...\" }\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:85
msgid "`abiVersion`"
msgstr "`abiVersion`"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:87
msgid "Semver string (e.g. `\"0.5\"`, `\"0.5.3\"`, `\"^0.5\"`)."
msgstr "Semver 字符串（例如 `\"0.5\"`、`\"0.5.3\"`、`\"^0.5\"`）。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:89
msgid ""
"The compiler interprets this as a range. The range must include the bundled "
"`perry-ffi`'s exact version. A wrapper declaring `\"0.5\"` loads under any "
"`0.5.x` Perry; one declaring `\"0.5.3\"` loads only when the runtime is "
"exactly `0.5.3`."
msgstr ""
"编译器将其作为一个范围解释。该范围必须包含捆绑的 `perry-ffi` 的精确版本。声明 `\"0.5\"` 的封装可在任何 `0.5.x` 版本的 "
"Perry 下加载；声明 `\"0.5.3\"` 的封装则只在运行时恰好为 `0.5.3` 时加载。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:94
msgid "When the runtime fails the range check, compilation aborts with:"
msgstr "当运行时未通过该范围检查时，编译会以以下信息中止："

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:96
msgid ""
"```\n"
"error: native library `<package>` declares perry-ffi ABI \"0.5\"\n"
"         but this Perry build ships perry-ffi 0.6.1.\n"
"       Update the package or use an older Perry release.\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:102 src/plugins/native-extensions.md:88
msgid "`functions`"
msgstr "`functions`"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:104
