"如果 `node_modules` 中没有匹配项，Perry 会查阅其内置的 well-known 绑定表（见 #466 Phase 4）—— "
"同样的规范适用于内置封装。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:449
msgid "None of the above match → resolution error."
msgstr "以上都未命中 → 解析错误。"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:451
