msgstr "浏览器标签没有托盘等价物。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:76
msgid "Click vs. Menu"
msgstr "点击 vs. 菜单"

#: src/ui/tray.md:78
msgid ""
"Different desktops have different click conventions; Perry exposes both "
"hooks so a single TypeScript app can do the right thing everywhere:"
msgstr "不同桌面环境有不同的点击约定；Perry 同时暴露这两种钩子，以便单一 TypeScript 应用在各处都能做正确的事："

#: src/ui/tray.md:81
msgid "Left-click"
msgstr "左键点击"

#: src/ui/tray.md:81
msgid "Right-click"
msgstr "右键点击"

#: src/ui/tray.md:83 src/ui/tray.md:84 src/ui/tray.md:85
msgid "Pops the attached menu"
msgstr "弹出附加的菜单"

#: src/ui/tray.md:83
msgid "Same as left-click"
msgstr "与左键点击相同"

#: src/ui/tray.md:84
msgid "Fires `onClick`"
msgstr "触发 `onClick`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:85 src/container/overview.md:28
msgid "**Linux**"
msgstr "**Linux**"

#: src/ui/tray.md:85
msgid "Fires `onClick` (KSNI `activate`)"
msgstr "触发 `onClick`（KSNI `activate`）"

#: src/ui/tray.md:87
msgid ""
"The typical pattern: use `onClick` to \"show / focus the main window\" and "
"`attachMenu` for the user-facing actions. macOS users will see the menu pop "
"on every click, which is the platform-native behavior."
msgstr ""
"典型用法：用 `onClick` 来“显示 / 聚焦主窗口”，用 `attachMenu` 处理面向用户的操作。在 macOS "
"上每次点击都会弹出菜单，这是平台原生行为。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:91
msgid "Common Patterns"
msgstr "常见模式"

#: src/ui/tray.md:93
msgid "Background app (no Dock icon, tray-only)"
msgstr "后台应用（无 Dock 图标，仅托盘）"

#: src/ui/tray.md:95
msgid ""
"On macOS, set the activation policy to `\"accessory\"` so the app has no "
"Dock icon and lives only as a tray-resident process. (See the [platform "
"docs](../platforms/macos.md) for activation-policy details.)"
msgstr ""
"在 macOS 上，将激活策略设置为 `\"accessory\"`，应用就不会有 Dock "
"图标，仅作为常驻托盘的进程存在。（详见[平台文档](../platforms/macos.md)关于激活策略的说明。）"

#: src/ui/tray.md:99
msgid "Building the menu after the tray"
msgstr "在创建托盘后再构建菜单"

#: src/ui/tray.md:101
msgid ""
"The menu lookup on every backend happens at click time, not at attach time. "
"This means you can rebuild the menu (`menuClear` + fresh `menuAddItem` "
"calls) between user clicks — the new menu wins on the next click without re-"
"attaching."
msgstr ""
"每个后端的菜单查找都发生在点击时，而不是在 attach 时。也就是说，你可以在用户点击之间重建菜单（`menuClear` + 新的 "
"`menuAddItem` 调用）——下一次点击时会用上新菜单，无需重新 attach。"

