msgid ""
"[Menus](menus.md) — Full menu / submenu / shortcut API used by "
"`trayAttachMenu`"
msgstr "[菜单](menus.md) — `trayAttachMenu` 使用的完整菜单 / 子菜单 / 快捷键 API"

