msgstr "`WebView2` 通过 `webview2-com`（固定为 `windows = \"0.58\"`）"

#: src/ui/webview.md:200
msgid ""
"A STATIC host HWND becomes the widget handle; `ICoreWebView2Controller` "
"binds to it. WebView2's two-stage async init is wrapped synchronously by "
"pumping the message queue with a 10s timeout — `WebView({...})` blocks until"
" the widget is live, so the first navigation isn't racing init. `WM_SIZE` is"
" subclassed on the host HWND and forwards bounds to `SetBounds` so the "
"surface tracks layout-engine resizes. Requires the WebView2 runtime, which "
"ships preinstalled on Windows 10+ and Windows Server 2019+."
msgstr ""
"一个静态宿主 HWND 成为组件句柄；`ICoreWebView2Controller` 绑定到它。WebView2 的两阶段异步初始化通过以 10 "
"秒超时抽取消息队列来同步封装——`WebView({...})` 会阻塞直到组件就绪，因此首次导航不会与初始化产生竞争。宿主 HWND 上子类化了 "
"`WM_SIZE`，并将边界转发给 `SetBounds`，使渲染面跟随布局引擎的尺寸调整。需要 WebView2 运行时，Windows 10+ 及 "
"Windows Server 2019+ 已预装。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:201
msgid "`WebKitGTK 6.0` via `webkit6 = \"=0.4\"`"
msgstr "`WebKitGTK 6.0` 通过 `webkit6 = \"=0.4\"`"

#: src/ui/webview.md:201
msgid ""
"Real implementation. `decide-policy::navigation-action` is the sync "
"intercept. Build dep: `libwebkitgtk-6.0-dev` (Ubuntu 22.10+ / Debian 12+)."
msgstr ""
"真实实现。`decide-policy::navigation-action` "
"是同步拦截点。构建依赖：`libwebkitgtk-6.0-dev`（Ubuntu 22.10+ / Debian 12+）。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:202
msgid "`android.webkit.WebView` via JNI"
msgstr "`android.webkit.WebView` 通过 JNI"

#: src/ui/webview.md:202
msgid ""
"`PerryWebViewClient.kt` (deployed alongside the runtime APK) bridges "
"`shouldOverrideUrlLoading` / `onPageFinished` / `onReceivedError` back to "
"native Rust. Full callback parity with the Apple / Windows / GTK4 backends. "
"Ephemeral isolation is best-effort — Android WebView shares storage process-"
"wide; `CookieManager.removeAllCookies(null)` + `WebStorage.deleteAllData()` "
"runs at create when requested."
msgstr ""
"`PerryWebViewClient.kt`（与运行时 APK 一同部署）将 `shouldOverrideUrlLoading` / "
"`onPageFinished` / `onReceivedError` 桥接回原生 Rust。与 Apple / Windows / GTK4 "
"后端完整回调对等。临时隔离为尽力而为——Android WebView 进程范围共享存储；请求时会在创建时运行 "
"`CookieManager.removeAllCookies(null)` + `WebStorage.deleteAllData()`。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:203
msgid "sandboxed `<iframe>`"
msgstr "沙盒化 `<iframe>`"

#: src/ui/webview.md:203
msgid ""
"`sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-forms allow-popups\"`. "
"`onShouldNavigate` is best-effort (cross-origin URLs the iframe navigates to"
" are unreachable from JS for security reasons); `onLoaded` fires from the "
"iframe's `load` event; `onError` from `error` (same-origin only). "
"`webviewEvaluateJs` only works on same-origin frames. UA is browser-"
"controlled. See \"Cross-origin messaging\" below."
msgstr ""
"`sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-forms allow-"
"popups\"`。`onShouldNavigate` 为尽力而为（出于安全原因，iframe 导航到的跨源 URL 无法从 JS "
"访问）；`onLoaded` 由 iframe 的 `load` 事件触发；`onError` 由 `error` "
"触发（仅同源）。`webviewEvaluateJs` 仅适用于同源框架。UA 由浏览器控制。参见下方\"跨源消息传递\"。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:204
msgid "**tvOS / watchOS**"
msgstr "**tvOS / watchOS**"

#: src/ui/webview.md:204
msgid "stub"
msgstr "存根"

#: src/ui/webview.md:204
msgid ""
"All 14 FFIs link as no-ops returning `0`. The widget is invisible; cross-"
"platform code compiles unchanged."
msgstr "所有 14 个 FFI 链接为返回 `0` 的空操作。该组件不可见；跨平台代码无需修改即可编译。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:206
msgid "Cross-Origin Messaging (Web Target)"
msgstr "跨源消息传递（Web 目标）"

#: src/ui/webview.md:208
msgid ""
"On the web target, the embedded iframe can `window.parent.postMessage` out, "
"and the host can `window.addEventListener(\"message\", ...)` to receive. "
"This is a **browser-only** pattern — native targets don't expose "
"`postMessage` (that's the Tauri / Electron path Perry's WebView deliberately"
" avoids)."
msgstr ""
"在 web 目标上，嵌入的 iframe 可通过 `window.parent.postMessage` 向外发送消息，宿主可通过 "
"`window.addEventListener(\"message\", ...)` 接收。这是**仅限浏览器**的模式——原生目标不暴露 "
"`postMessage`（那是 Perry WebView 刻意回避的 Tauri / Electron 路径）。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:214
msgid "The portable contract that works on every target:"
msgstr "适用于所有目标的可移植约定："

#: src/ui/webview.md:216
msgid "Push state **in** with `webviewEvaluateJs(wv, \"window.someHook(...)\")`."
msgstr "通过 `webviewEvaluateJs(wv, \"window.someHook(...)\")` **推入**状态。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:217
msgid ""
"Pull state **out** by intercepting a known callback URL in "
"`onShouldNavigate`."
msgstr "通过在 `onShouldNavigate` 中拦截已知回调 URL 来**拉取**状态。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:220
msgid "Common Pitfalls"
msgstr "常见陷阱"

#: src/ui/webview.md:222
msgid ""
"**Don't reuse one `WebView` for unrelated sessions.** Cookie isolation is "
"per-WebView, not per-call. If you need to log a different user in, call "
"`webviewClearCookies(handle)` first or destroy and recreate the widget."
msgstr ""
"**不要将一个 `WebView` 复用于不相关的会话。** Cookie 隔离是按 WebView 而非按调用划分的。若需要以不同用户登录，请先调用 "
"`webviewClearCookies(handle)` 或销毁并重新创建组件。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:226
msgid ""
"**`onShouldNavigate` runs on the main thread.** Keep it cheap — it blocks "
"the navigation until you return. Heavy work belongs in `onLoaded` or off-"
"thread via `spawn`."
msgstr ""
"**`onShouldNavigate` 在主线程上运行。** 保持轻量——它会阻塞导航直到返回。繁重工作应放在 `onLoaded` 中或通过 "
"`spawn` 移至线程外。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:229
msgid ""
"**WebView2 runtime requirement on older Windows.** WebView2 is preinstalled "
"on Windows 10 1803+ and Windows Server 2019+. On older builds the runtime "
"needs to be installed separately (Microsoft ships an evergreen "
"bootstrapper)."
msgstr ""
"**旧版 Windows 上的 WebView2 运行时要求。** WebView2 预装于 Windows 10 1803+ 及 Windows "
"Server 2019+。在更旧的版本上需要单独安装运行时（微软提供常青引导程序）。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:233
msgid ""
"**No bidirectional RPC.** If you find yourself round-tripping structured "
"data through `webviewEvaluateJs` callbacks, you're past the design scope — "
"pick Tauri / Electron instead, or move the logic out of the embedded page."
msgstr ""
"**无双向 RPC。** 如果你发现自己通过 `webviewEvaluateJs` 回调来回传递结构化数据，说明已超出设计范围——请改用 Tauri "
"/ Electron，或将逻辑移出嵌入页面。"

#: src/ui/webview.md:241
msgid ""
"[State Management](state.md) — React to `onLoaded` / `onError` from the rest"
" of the UI"
msgstr "[状态管理](state.md) — 从 UI 其余部分响应 `onLoaded` / `onError`"

#: src/ui/webview.md:242
msgid ""
"[Multi-Window](multi-window.md) — Pop a fresh window with a WebView for "
"isolated sessions"
msgstr "[多窗口](multi-window.md) — 弹出带有 WebView 的新窗口以进行隔离会话"

#: src/tui/overview.md:1
msgid "Terminal UI Overview"
msgstr "终端 UI 概述"

#: src/tui/overview.md:3
msgid ""
"`perry/tui` is a native terminal-UI engine built into the Perry runtime. It "
"targets the same use cases as [ink](https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink) "
"(interactive CLIs, dashboards, REPLs, log viewers) but compiles to native "
"code — no Node, no React reconciler, no fiber tree. Your code runs as a "
"single static binary that does a double-buffered ANSI diff each frame."
msgstr ""
"`perry/tui` 是内置于 Perry 运行时的原生终端 UI 引擎。它面向与 "
"[ink](https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink) 相同的使用场景（交互式 "
"CLI、仪表盘、REPL、日志查看器），但编译为原生代码——无需 Node、无 React 协调器、无 fiber "
"树。你的代码作为单个静态二进制文件运行，每帧进行双缓冲 ANSI 差分更新。"

#: src/tui/overview.md:5
msgid "When to use `perry/tui`"
msgstr "何时使用 `perry/tui`"

#: src/tui/overview.md:7
msgid "You want…"
msgstr "你想要……"

#: src/tui/overview.md:7
msgid "Use"
msgstr "使用"

#: src/tui/overview.md:9
msgid "An interactive CLI tool (prompts, menus, live progress)"
msgstr "交互式 CLI 工具（提示、菜单、实时进度）"

#: src/tui/overview.md:9 src/tui/overview.md:10
msgid "**`perry/tui`**"
msgstr "**`perry/tui`**"

#: src/tui/overview.md:10
msgid "A long-running terminal dashboard / log viewer"
msgstr "长期运行的终端仪表盘 / 日志查看器"

#: src/tui/overview.md:11
msgid "A native desktop / mobile app"
msgstr "原生桌面 / 移动应用"

#: src/tui/overview.md:11
msgid "[`perry/ui`](../ui/overview.md)"
msgstr "[`perry/ui`](../ui/overview.md)"

#: src/tui/overview.md:12
msgid "A one-shot script that just prints to stdout"
msgstr "仅打印到 stdout 的一次性脚本"

#: src/tui/overview.md:12
msgid "Plain `console.log`"
msgstr "普通 `console.log`"

#: src/tui/overview.md:14
msgid ""
"`perry/tui` enters the terminal's [alternate screen "
"buffer](https://invisible-island.net/xterm/ctlseqs/ctlseqs.html#h2-The-"
"Alternate-Screen-Buffer) (so your scrollback isn't polluted), captures raw-"
"mode keypresses, and re-renders only the cells that changed between frames. "
"The cell grid is a packed `Vec<Cell>` so an 80×24 terminal fits in ~15 KB — "
"well within L2."
msgstr ""
"`perry/tui` 进入终端的[备用屏幕缓冲区](https://invisible-"
"island.net/xterm/ctlseqs/ctlseqs.html#h2-The-Alternate-Screen-"
"Buffer)（避免污染滚动历史），捕获原始模式按键，并仅重绘帧间发生变化的单元格。单元格网格是一个紧凑的 `Vec<Cell>`，80×24 终端约占"
" ~15 KB——完全在 L2 范围内。"

#: src/tui/overview.md:18
msgid ""
"The smallest interactive `perry/tui` program — a counter that increments on "
"`+`, decrements on `-`, and quits on `q`:"
msgstr "最小的交互式 `perry/tui` 程序——按 `+` 递增、按 `-` 递减、按 `q` 退出的计数器："

#: src/tui/overview.md:20
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { Box, Text, useState, useInput, run, exit } from \"perry/tui\";\n"
"\n"
"run(() => {\n"
"    const [n, setN] = useState(0);\n"
"\n"
"    useInput((s: string) => {\n"
"        if (s === \"+\") setN(n + 1);\n"
"        if (s === \"-\") setN(n - 1);\n"
"        if (s === \"q\") exit();\n"
"    });\n"
"\n"
"    return Box([Text(\"count: \" + n)]);\n"
"});\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/overview.md:42
msgid ""
"The component closure is called every render. Hooks "
"(`useState`/`useInput`/etc.) bind to a per-frame call-site index so the "
"second render's `useState(0)` at the same position reads back what the first"
" render wrote — same model as React. The run loop re-renders when any state "
"setter is called and idles between renders."
msgstr ""
"组件闭包在每次渲染时被调用。Hook（`useState` / `useInput` 等）绑定到每帧的调用位置索引，因此第二次渲染时同一位置的 "
"`useState(0)` 会读回第一次渲染写入的值——与 React 模型相同。运行循环在任意状态设置器被调用时重新渲染，并在渲染之间空闲。"

#: src/tui/overview.md:46
msgid "Perry's TUI uses the same authoring model as ink:"
msgstr "Perry 的 TUI 使用与 ink 相同的编写模型："

#: src/tui/overview.md:48
msgid ""
"**Components are functions** that return a widget tree. The function is "
"called every render; the tree it returns is diffed against the previous "
"frame's tree and only changed terminal cells get rewritten."
msgstr "**组件是函数**，返回一个组件树。函数在每次渲染时被调用；返回的树与上一帧的树进行差分，只有发生变化的终端单元格才会被重写。"

#: src/tui/overview.md:49
msgid ""
"**State lives in hooks** (`useState`, `useRef`, `useMemo`). A change "
"triggers a re-render automatically."
msgstr "**状态存储在 hook 中**（`useState`、`useRef`、`useMemo`）。状态变化会自动触发重新渲染。"

#: src/tui/overview.md:50
msgid ""
"**Layout uses flexbox** (powered by "
"[Taffy](https://github.com/DioxusLabs/taffy)) — `flexDirection: \"row\" | "
"\"column\"`, `gap`, `padding`, `justifyContent`, `alignItems`, `flexGrow`, "
"etc."
msgstr ""
"**布局使用 flexbox**（由 [Taffy](https://github.com/DioxusLabs/taffy) "
"驱动）——`flexDirection: \"row\" | "
"\"column\"`、`gap`、`padding`、`justifyContent`、`alignItems`、`flexGrow` 等。"

#: src/tui/overview.md:52
msgid ""
"If you've used ink, the only real difference at the surface is the **factory"
" call form** — `Box({…opts}, [children])` instead of `<Box>…</Box>` JSX. JSX"
" works for user-defined component functions today (`<App />` calls "
"`App(props)`), but the `<Box>` / `<Text>` intrinsics still need the "
"function-call form until a compile-time JSX→intrinsic rewriter lands."
msgstr ""
"如果你用过 ink，表面上唯一真正的区别是**工厂调用形式**——`Box({…opts}, [children])` 而非 JSX 的 "
"`<Box>…</Box>`。JSX 目前适用于用户定义的组件函数（`<App />` 会调用 `App(props)`），但 `<Box>` / "
"`<Text>` 内置组件仍需使用函数调用形式，直到编译时 JSX→内置重写器落地。"

#: src/tui/overview.md:54
msgid "Architecture in one paragraph"
msgstr "架构概述（一段话）"

#: src/tui/overview.md:56
msgid ""
"`run(component)` enters the alt screen, enables raw mode on stdin, spawns a "
"reader thread, and loops: reset hook index → call the component closure → "
"diff the returned widget tree against the front buffer → emit minimal ANSI "
"to reconcile → drain pending keypresses (dispatching to `useInput` handlers "
"and the focus ring) → if any state changed, immediately re-render; else idle"
" 16 ms. Exit happens when `exit()` (or `useApp().exit()`) flips a flag the "
"loop checks at the top of every iteration. On exit, raw mode is restored and"
" the alt screen is left so your terminal returns to exactly the state it was"
" in before the program ran."
msgstr ""
"`run(component)` 进入备用屏幕，对 stdin 启用原始模式，启动读取线程，并循环执行：重置 hook 索引 → 调用组件闭包 → "
"将返回的 widget 树与前端缓冲区做差异对比 → 输出最少量 ANSI 序列进行协调 → 消耗待处理的按键事件（分发给 `useInput` "
"处理器和焦点环）→ 如果状态发生变化则立即重新渲染；否则空闲 16 毫秒。当 `exit()`（或 "
"`useApp().exit()`）翻转一个标志位时，循环在每次迭代开头检测到该标志后退出。退出时，原始模式被恢复，备用屏幕被关闭，终端状态恢复到程序运行前的状态。"

