msgstr "`Box(opts?, children?)`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:7
msgid ""
"A flexbox container. Holds any number of children laid out by direction, "
"gap, padding, and alignment rules."
msgstr "一个 flexbox 容器，可容纳任意数量的子节点，按方向、间距、内边距和对齐规则进行布局。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:9
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { Box, Text } from \"perry/tui\";\n"
"\n"
"// Bare children — vertical column by default.\n"
"Box([Text(\"first\"), Text(\"second\")]);\n"
"\n"
"// With style.\n"
"Box({ flexDirection: \"row\", gap: 2, padding: 1 }, [\n"
"    Text(\"left\"),\n"
"    Text(\"right\"),\n"
"]);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { Box, Text } from \"perry/tui\";\n"
"\n"
"// 仅传子节点——默认垂直排列。\n"
"Box([Text(\"first\"), Text(\"second\")]);\n"
"\n"
"// 带样式。\n"
"Box({ flexDirection: \"row\", gap: 2, padding: 1 }, [\n"
"    Text(\"left\"),\n"
"    Text(\"right\"),\n"
"]);\n"
"```"

