" modern terminal."
msgstr ""
"命名颜色：`black`、`red`、`green`、`yellow`、`blue`、`magenta`、`cyan`、`white`，以及对应的 "
"`bright*` 变体。Truecolor（`#rrggbb`）在所有现代终端上均可使用。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:68 src/platforms/harmonyos.md:41
msgid "`Spacer()`"
msgstr "`Spacer()`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:70
msgid ""
"A zero-content widget with `flexGrow: 1` baked in. Push siblings to the "
"edges of a flex container without spelling out the grow factor:"
msgstr "一个内置 `flexGrow: 1` 的空内容 widget。可将兄弟节点推到 flex 容器的两端，无需显式指定 grow 系数："

#: src/tui/widgets.md:72
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"Box({ flexDirection: \"row\" }, [\n"
"    Text(\"left\"),\n"
"    Spacer(),\n"
"    Text(\"right\"),\n"
"]);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"Box({ flexDirection: \"row\" }, [\n"
"    Text(\"left\"),\n"
"    Spacer(),\n"
"    Text(\"right\"),\n"
"]);\n"
"```"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:80
msgid "`Input(value, cursor?)`"
msgstr "`Input(value, cursor?)`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:82
msgid ""
"A single-line text-input widget. Render a string with an optional inline "
"cursor position (0-indexed); pair with `useState` for the buffer and "
"`useInput` to drive it."
msgstr ""
"单行文本输入 widget。渲染一个字符串，并可选择性地显示内联光标位置（从 0 开始索引）；配合 `useState` 管理缓冲区，配合 "
"`useInput` 驱动输入。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:84
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [buf, setBuf] = useState(\"\");\n"
"const [cur, setCur] = useState(0);\n"
"useInput((s) => { /* … update buf + cur on keypress … */ });\n"
"return Input(buf, cur);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [buf, setBuf] = useState(\"\");\n"
"const [cur, setCur] = useState(0);\n"
"useInput((s) => { /* … update buf + cur on keypress … */ });\n"
"return Input(buf, cur);\n"
"```"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:91
msgid ""
"`perry/tui` doesn't ship a full line editor — it gives you the rendering "
"primitive and you wire the keys yourself. See the chat REPL in "
"[Examples](examples.md) for a typical input loop."
msgstr ""
"`perry/tui` 不内置完整的行编辑器——它提供渲染原语，按键逻辑由你自行接入。典型的输入循环示例请参见[示例](examples.md)中的聊天"
" REPL。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:93
msgid "`TextArea(value)`"
msgstr "`TextArea(value)`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:95
msgid "A multi-line text widget. Same shape as `Input` but accepts newlines."
msgstr "多行文本 widget。与 `Input` 形态相同，但支持换行符。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:97
msgid "`List(items, selected?)`"
msgstr "`List(items, selected?)`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:99
msgid ""
"A vertically-laid list of strings, with optional highlighted-row index."
msgstr "垂直排列的字符串列表，支持可选的高亮行索引。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:101
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"List([\"Apple\", \"Banana\", \"Cherry\"], 1);  // \"Banana\" highlighted\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"List([\"Apple\", \"Banana\", \"Cherry\"], 1);  // \"Banana\" 高亮显示\n"
"```"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:105
msgid "`Select(items, selected?)`"
msgstr "`Select(items, selected?)`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:107
msgid ""
"Like `List` but with selection indicators (`▸` next to the focused row)."
msgstr "与 `List` 类似，但在焦点行旁显示选中指示符（`▸`）。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:109
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [idx, setIdx] = useState(0);\n"
"useInput((s) => {\n"
"    if (s === \"\\x1b[A\" /* up */ ) setIdx(Math.max(0, idx - 1));\n"
"    if (s === \"\\x1b[B\" /* down */) setIdx(Math.min(items.length - 1, idx + 1));\n"
"});\n"
"return Select(items, idx);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [idx, setIdx] = useState(0);\n"
"useInput((s) => {\n"
"    if (s === \"\\x1b[A\" /* up */ ) setIdx(Math.max(0, idx - 1));\n"
"    if (s === \"\\x1b[B\" /* down */) setIdx(Math.min(items.length - 1, idx + 1));\n"
"});\n"
"return Select(items, idx);\n"
"```"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:118
msgid "`Spinner(frame)`"
msgstr "`Spinner(frame)`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:120
msgid ""
"A static spinner character — `- \\ | /` cycling through frames 0–3. Caller "
"bumps `frame` from a state counter to animate."
msgstr "静态旋转字符——在帧 0–3 之间循环显示 `- \\ | /`。调用方通过状态计数器递增 `frame` 来实现动画效果。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:122
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [tick, setTick] = useState(0);\n"
"// On every Enter (or however you want to advance):\n"
"setTick(tick + 1);\n"
"return Box([Spinner(tick), Text(\" working…\")]);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [tick, setTick] = useState(0);\n"
"// 每次按 Enter（或任意你希望推进的方式）：\n"
"setTick(tick + 1);\n"
"return Box([Spinner(tick), Text(\" working…\")]);\n"
"```"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:129
msgid ""
"`Spinner(0)` is a static `-` — useful as a stable bullet if you don't want "
"animation."
msgstr "`Spinner(0)` 是静态的 `-`——如果不需要动画，可用作稳定的项目符号。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:131
msgid ""
"For true wall-clock animation, see `AnimatedSpinner({ interval, frames })` "
"which runs its own internal tick (it advances when the render loop polls "
"between frames)."
msgstr ""
"如需真正的挂钟动画，请参阅 `AnimatedSpinner({ interval, frames })`，它内部维护自己的 "
"tick（在渲染循环帧间轮询时自动推进）。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:133
msgid "`ProgressBar(filled, total, width?)`"
msgstr "`ProgressBar(filled, total, width?)`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:135
msgid "A simple horizontal bar."
msgstr "一个简单的水平进度条。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:137
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"ProgressBar(7, 10);          // ████████░░ at default width\n"
"ProgressBar(50, 100, 40);    // 40-cell wide bar\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"ProgressBar(7, 10);          // 默认宽度的 ████████░░\n"
"ProgressBar(50, 100, 40);    // 40 单元格宽的进度条\n"
"```"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:142
msgid "`Table({ headers, rows, selected? })`"
msgstr "`Table({ headers, rows, selected? })`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:144
msgid ""
"A bordered table. `headers` is a string array; `rows` is an array of string "
"arrays."
msgstr "带边框的表格。`headers` 为字符串数组；`rows` 为字符串数组的数组。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:146
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"Table({\n"
"    headers: [\"Name\", \"Status\", \"Latency\"],\n"
"    rows: [\n"
"        [\"api-east\", \"OK\", \"12ms\"],\n"
"        [\"api-west\", \"DEGRADED\", \"412ms\"],\n"
"    ],\n"
"    selected: 1,\n"
"});\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"Table({\n"
"    headers: [\"Name\", \"Status\", \"Latency\"],\n"
"    rows: [\n"
"        [\"api-east\", \"OK\", \"12ms\"],\n"
"        [\"api-west\", \"DEGRADED\", \"412ms\"],\n"
"    ],\n"
"    selected: 1,\n"
"});\n"
"```"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:157
msgid "`Tabs({ tabs, active, body })`"
msgstr "`Tabs({ tabs, active, body })`"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:159
msgid ""
"A horizontal tab bar over a body widget. `body` is an array parallel to "
"`tabs` — only the active tab's body is rendered."
msgstr "在主体 widget 上方显示水平选项卡栏。`body` 是与 `tabs` 并行的数组——只渲染当前激活选项卡对应的主体内容。"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:161
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [active, setActive] = useState(0);\n"
"Tabs({\n"
"    tabs: [\"Files\", \"Search\", \"Settings\"],\n"
"    active,\n"
"    body: [filesView, searchView, settingsView],\n"
"});\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [active, setActive] = useState(0);\n"
"Tabs({\n"
"    tabs: [\"Files\", \"Search\", \"Settings\"],\n"
"    active,\n"
"    body: [filesView, searchView, settingsView],\n"
"});\n"
"```"

#: src/tui/widgets.md:172
msgid ""
"For state + event hooks (the React-shape "
"`useState`/`useInput`/`useApp`/etc.), see [Hooks](hooks.md). For complete "
"worked examples, see [Examples](examples.md)."
msgstr ""
"有关状态与事件 hook（React 风格的 `useState`/`useInput`/`useApp` 等），请参见 "
"[Hooks](hooks.md)。完整示例请参见[示例](examples.md)。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:3
msgid ""
"`perry/tui` implements the React-shape hook API on top of a call-site-"
"indexed slot pool. Each `useXxx` call gets the slot at its position in the "
"component body; the run loop resets the index at the top of every frame, so "
"the second render's `useState` at the same position reads back what the "
"first wrote."
msgstr ""
"`perry/tui` 在调用位置索引的 slot 池之上实现了 React 风格的 hook API。每个 `useXxx` "
"调用获取其在组件体中位置对应的 slot；运行循环在每帧开头重置索引，因此第二次渲染时，同一位置的 `useState` 会读回第一次写入的值。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:5
msgid ""
"This is the same rule-of-hooks model ink/React use: **call hooks in the same"
" order on every render**. Don't call them inside `if`/loops — the slot index"
" would skew and you'd read the wrong slot. Slot kinds are tagged (`State` / "
"`Effect` / `Memo` / `Ref` / `Focus`); calling `useState` at a position "
"previously used by `useMemo` re-tags the slot rather than corrupting it, but"
" the value resets."
msgstr ""
"这与 ink/React 使用的 hook 规则模型相同：**在每次渲染时以相同顺序调用 hook**。不要在 `if`/循环内调用它们——slot "
"索引会错位，导致读取错误的 slot。Slot 类型有标记（`State` / `Effect` / `Memo` / `Ref` / "
"`Focus`）；在之前被 `useMemo` 使用过的位置调用 `useState` 会重新标记该 slot 而不会导致数据损坏，但值会被重置。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:7
msgid "`useState(initial)`"
msgstr "`useState(initial)`"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:9
msgid "Per-frame state cell. Returns `[value, setter]`."
msgstr "逐帧状态单元。返回 `[value, setter]`。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:11
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [count, setCount] = useState(0);\n"
"// Later, from an input handler:\n"
"setCount(count + 1);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [count, setCount] = useState(0);\n"
"// 之后，在输入处理器中：\n"
"setCount(count + 1);\n"
"```"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:17
msgid ""
"The setter writes through to the slot's bits and flips a global "
"`STATE_DIRTY` flag — the run loop sees it after `useInput` drains and "
"immediately re-renders without sleeping."
msgstr ""
"setter 将值写入槽的位并翻转全局 `STATE_DIRTY` 标志——运行循环在 `useInput` "
"排空后检测到该标志，立即重新渲染，无需休眠。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:19
msgid ""
"Setting the same value twice (bit-identical) is a no-op — `STATE_DIRTY` "
"stays clear and the loop idles. This avoids the \"render storm\" pattern "
"where unconditional `setX(prev)` calls would loop forever."
msgstr ""
"连续两次设置相同值（位级相同）为空操作——`STATE_DIRTY` 保持清除，循环空闲。这避免了“渲染风暴”模式：无条件调用 `setX(prev)`"
" 会导致无限循环。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:21
msgid "Stale-closure gotcha"
msgstr "过期闭包陷阱"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:23
msgid ""
"The setter captured by a `useInput` handler reads `value` from **that "
"frame's closure**, not from the slot. If many bytes arrive in one frame "
"(paste, typing fast), the handler fires N times with the same `value`:"
msgstr ""
"`useInput` 处理函数捕获的 setter 从**该帧的闭包**中读取 "
"`value`，而非从槽中读取。如果一帧内到达多个字节（粘贴、快速输入），处理函数会以相同的 `value` 触发 N 次："

#: src/tui/hooks.md:25
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const [n, setN] = useState(0);\n"
"useInput((s) => { if (s === \"+\") setN(n + 1); });\n"
"// User pastes \"+++\" — handler fires 3× with n=0, all three set the slot to 1.\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/hooks.md:31
msgid ""
"If you need a functional setter for this case, use `useRef` as a mirror:"
msgstr "如果此场景需要函数式 setter，可以用 `useRef` 作为镜像："

#: src/tui/hooks.md:33
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const buf = useRef(\"\");\n"
"const [, redraw] = useState(0);\n"
"useInput((s) => {\n"
"    if (s.length === 1 && s >= \" \" && s <= \"~\") {\n"
"        buf.set(buf.get() + s);     // canonical buffer (no stale capture)\n"
"        redraw(buf.get().length);   // trigger re-render\n"
"    }\n"
"});\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/hooks.md:44
msgid "`useEffect(fn, deps?)`"
msgstr "`useEffect(fn, deps?)`"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:46
msgid ""
"Run a side effect after first render, and again whenever a dep changes."
msgstr "在首次渲染后执行副作用，并在依赖项变化时再次执行。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:48
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"useEffect(() => {\n"
"    // Run-once on mount.\n"
"    fetchInitialData();\n"
"}, []);\n"
"\n"
"useEffect(() => {\n"
"    // Re-run whenever `query` changes.\n"
"    runSearch(query);\n"
"}, [query]);\n"
"\n"
"useEffect(() => {\n"
"    // No deps array → run every render. Rarely what you want.\n"
"});\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/hooks.md:64
msgid ""
"Deps are compared by bit-identity using an FNV-1a hash of the deps' NaN-"
"boxed values. An empty array `[]` hashes to a stable non-zero value, giving "
"the React \"run once\" behaviour; passing no array runs the effect every "
"render."
msgstr ""
"依赖项通过对其 NaN-boxed 值进行 FNV-1a 哈希的位级相同性进行比较。空数组 `[]` 哈希为稳定的非零值，实现 React "
"的“只运行一次”行为；不传数组则每次渲染都执行副作用。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:66
msgid ""
"The effect closure runs synchronously inside the component call. Cleanup-on-"
"dep-change (returning a cleanup function) is **not** wired yet — the return "
"value is ignored."
msgstr "effect 闭包在组件调用内部同步运行。依赖项变化时的清理（返回清理函数）**尚未**连接——返回值会被忽略。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:68
msgid "`useMemo(fn, deps)`"
msgstr "`useMemo(fn, deps)`"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:70
msgid ""
"Cache the result of `fn()` keyed by `deps`. Same hash convention as "
"`useEffect`."
msgstr "以 `deps` 为键缓存 `fn()` 的结果。哈希约定与 `useEffect` 相同。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:79
msgid ""
"Recomputes on first call or when `deps` change. Otherwise returns the cached"
" value."
msgstr "在首次调用或 `deps` 变化时重新计算，否则返回缓存值。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:81
msgid "`useRef(initial)`"
msgstr "`useRef(initial)`"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:83
msgid ""
"A stable mutable cell that doesn't trigger re-renders. Use for values you "
"want to mutate but don't want to drive the UI."
msgstr "一个稳定的可变单元，不会触发重新渲染。用于你想修改但不希望驱动 UI 的值。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:85
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const renderCount = useRef(0);\n"
"renderCount.set(renderCount.get() + 1);   // does NOT flip STATE_DIRTY\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/hooks.md:90
msgid ""
"`.get()` reads, `.set(v)` writes. Identity is stable across renders — "
"calling `useRef(0)` at the same position returns the same handle every time,"
" so closures captured in `useEffect` / `useInput` always see the latest "
"value."
msgstr ""
"`.get()` 读取，`.set(v)` 写入。标识在渲染间保持稳定——在同一位置调用 `useRef(0)` 每次返回相同的句柄，因此在 "
"`useEffect` / `useInput` 中捕获的闭包始终能看到最新值。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:92
msgid ""
"Common pattern: use `useRef` as the canonical buffer for input that gets "
"typed at terminal speed, and pair with a throwaway `useState` to trigger "
"redraws (see the stale-closure gotcha above)."
msgstr ""
"常见模式：使用 `useRef` 作为以终端速度输入的规范缓冲区，并配合一次性的 `useState` 触发重绘（参见上方的过期闭包陷阱）。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:94
msgid "`useApp()`"
msgstr "`useApp()`"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:96
msgid "Returns a handle for imperative control of the run loop."
msgstr "返回一个用于命令式控制运行循环的句柄。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:98
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const app = useApp();\n"
"// Later:\n"
"app.exit();                    // tells run() to break at the top of the next iteration\n"
"await app.waitUntilExit();     // blocks until EXIT_FLAG is set (rare; usually `run` itself blocks)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/hooks.md:105
msgid ""
"The handle is stable — calling `useApp()` on every render returns the same "
"singleton. Wrap it in `useRef` if you want to stash it for a callback that "
"outlives the render."
msgstr ""
"该句柄是稳定的——每次渲染时调用 `useApp()` 返回同一个单例。如果你想将其存储到一个生命周期超过渲染的回调中，可以用 `useRef` 包裹。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:107
msgid "`useStdout()`"
msgstr "`useStdout()`"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:109
msgid "Terminal dimensions and a raw-write escape hatch."
msgstr "终端尺寸及原始写入转义通道。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:111
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const stdout = useStdout();\n"
"const cols = stdout.columns();    // terminal width in cells (falls back to 80 if not a TTY)\n"
"const rows = stdout.rows();       // height in cells (fallback 24)\n"
"stdout.write(\"raw bytes\\n\");      // bypass the cell-grid diff\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/hooks.md:118
msgid ""
"Use `columns`/`rows` to size dividers, truncate content to fit, or pick a "
"layout direction. `write` is rarely needed — almost everything should go "
"through widgets so the cell-grid diff can render it efficiently."
msgstr ""
"使用 `columns`/`rows` 来调整分隔符大小、截断内容以适应，或选择布局方向。`write` 很少需要——几乎所有内容都应通过 widget"
" 传递，以便单元格网格差异渲染能高效处理。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:120
msgid "`useFocus(autoFocus, isActive)`"
msgstr "`useFocus(autoFocus, isActive)`"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:122
msgid ""
"Register the calling widget as a focus candidate. Returns `1.0` when this "
"widget is the currently focused one, else `0.0` (treat as truthy/falsy)."
msgstr ""
"将调用该 hook 的 widget 注册为焦点候选。当该 widget 是当前焦点时返回 `1.0`，否则返回 `0.0`（视为真值/假值）。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:124
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const isFocused = useFocus(1 /* autoFocus */, 1 /* isActive */);\n"
"return Box({ flexDirection: \"row\" }, [\n"
"    Text(\"> \", isFocused ? { color: \"cyan\", bold: true } : { dimColor: true }),\n"
"    Text(\"name input\"),\n"
"]);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/hooks.md:132
msgid ""
"`autoFocus`: pass `1` for one widget to take focus on first render. "
"Subsequent `useFocus` calls with `autoFocus=1` are ignored once focus has "
"been claimed."
msgstr ""
"`autoFocus`：为某个 widget 传入 `1`，使其在首次渲染时获得焦点。一旦焦点已被占用，后续带 `autoFocus=1` 的 "
"`useFocus` 调用将被忽略。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:133
msgid ""
"`isActive`: pass `0` to remove this widget from the Tab cycle (e.g. a "
"disabled field)."
msgstr "`isActive`：传入 `0` 可将该 widget 从 Tab 循环中移除（例如禁用的字段）。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:135
msgid ""
"Tab and Shift-Tab cycle focus automatically — no boilerplate. The run loop's"
" input drain handles the `\\x09` / `\\x1b[Z` byte sequences before "
"forwarding them to your `useInput` handler."
msgstr ""
"Tab 和 Shift-Tab 会自动循环焦点——无需样板代码。运行循环的输入排空在将 `\\x09` / `\\x1b[Z` 字节序列转发到 "
"`useInput` 处理函数之前会先处理它们。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:137
msgid "For imperative focus control, pair with `useFocusManager()`:"
msgstr "如需命令式焦点控制，可配合 `useFocusManager()` 使用："

#: src/tui/hooks.md:139
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const focus = useFocusManager();\n"
"// Later:\n"
"focus.focusNext();\n"
"focus.focusPrevious();\n"
"focus.focus(id);   // by focus id (1-based, in registration order)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/hooks.md:147 src/tui/hooks.md:178
msgid "`useInput(handler)`"
msgstr "`useInput(handler)`"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:149
msgid ""
"Register a keypress handler. Called once per byte chunk arriving on stdin, "
"in raw mode."
msgstr "注册一个按键处理函数。每次 stdin 以原始模式接收到字节块时调用一次。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:151
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"useInput((s: string) => {\n"
"    if (s === \"\\x03\") app.exit();               // Ctrl+C\n"
"    if (s === \"\\r\" || s === \"\\n\") onSubmit();   // Enter\n"
"    if (s === \"\\x7f\" || s === \"\\b\") onErase();  // Backspace\n"
"    if (s === \"\\x1b[A\") onUpArrow();            // ANSI up\n"
"    if (s.length === 1 && s >= \" \" && s <= \"~\") onPrintable(s);\n"
"});\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/tui/hooks.md:161
msgid ""
"The `s` argument is the raw byte chunk as a string. ANSI escape sequences "
"like arrow keys arrive as a single chunk (`\\x1b[A`, `\\x1b[B`, `\\x1b[C`, "
"`\\x1b[D`); printable characters as one byte; control codes (Ctrl+C, Tab, "
"Enter, Backspace) as their literal byte."
msgstr ""
"`s` 参数是作为字符串的原始字节块。方向键等 ANSI "
"转义序列以单个块到达（`\\x1b[A`、`\\x1b[B`、`\\x1b[C`、`\\x1b[D`）；可打印字符为一个字节；控制码（Ctrl+C、Tab、Enter、Backspace）为其字面字节。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:163
msgid ""
"**Tab handling**: Tab (`\\x09`) and Shift-Tab (`\\x1b[Z`) cycle the focus "
"ring _before_ the handler is called. The handler still sees the byte, so you"
" can branch on it if you want custom Tab behaviour — but for the typical "
"\"Tab moves focus\" case the framework already did it."
msgstr ""
"**Tab 处理**：Tab（`\\x09`）和 Shift-"
"Tab（`\\x1b[Z`）在调用处理函数_之前_先循环焦点环。处理函数仍然能看到该字节，因此如果你想要自定义 Tab "
"行为可以进行分支处理——但对于典型的“Tab 移动焦点”场景，框架已自动完成。"

#: src/tui/hooks.md:165
msgid ""
"Only one handler is registered at a time (last `useInput` call wins). For "
"multiple focusable widgets, dispatch from one handler by checking "
"`useFocus`'s return."
msgstr ""
"每次只注册一个处理函数（最后一次 `useInput` 调用生效）。对于多个可聚焦的 widget，可以通过检查 `useFocus` "
"的返回值，从一个处理函数中分发。"

