"运行时会自动处理应用生命周期："

#: src/platforms/watchos.md:84
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { App, Text, VStack, Button } from \"perry/ui\"\n"
"\n"
"App({\n"
"    title: \"My Watch App\",\n"
"    width: 200,\n"
"    height: 200,\n"
"    body: VStack(8, [\n"
"        Text(\"Hello, Apple Watch!\"),\n"
"        Button(\"Tap me\", () => {\n"
"            console.log(\"Button tapped!\")\n"
