msgstr "备份方案"

#: src/container/volumes.md:158
msgid "The standard \"tar the volume into the host\" backup recipe:"
msgstr "将卷打包为 tar 并保存到宿主机的标准备份方法："

#: src/container/volumes.md:165
msgid "For a pure-Perry approach, drive that with `perry/container.run()`:"
msgstr "如需纯 Perry 方式，可使用 `perry/container.run()` 驱动："

#: src/container/volumes.md:167
