#: src/container/volumes.md:185
msgid "[Security](./security.md) — read-only mounts and ownership patterns."
msgstr "[安全性](./security.md) — 只读挂载与归属模式。"

#: src/container/security.md:3
msgid ""
"Containers don't isolate themselves; you isolate them. Perry exposes the "
"standard OCI security knobs on both `ContainerSpec` (single-container) and "
"`ComposeService` (orchestrated stacks), plus first-party support for "
"Sigstore / cosign image verification and a workload-graph policy tier API "
"for declarative isolation levels."
msgstr ""
"容器不会自我隔离；隔离是您的责任。Perry 在 `ContainerSpec`（单容器）和 `ComposeService`（编排 "
"stack）上都暴露了标准 OCI 安全旋钮，同时原生支持 Sigstore / cosign 镜像验证，以及用于声明式隔离级别的工作负载图策略层 "
"API。"

#: src/container/security.md:9
msgid "Per-container security knobs"
msgstr "容器级安全旋钮"

#: src/container/security.md:11
msgid ""
"The same set of fields work on `run()`, `create()`, and any service in a "
"compose `up()`:"
msgstr "以下字段在 `run()`、`create()` 以及 compose `up()` 中的任意服务上均可使用："

#: src/container/security.md:14
msgid "Cross-backend"
msgstr "跨后端"

#: src/container/security.md:16
msgid ""
"Mount the root filesystem as read-only. Forces all writable state to be in "
"declared volumes."
msgstr "将根文件系统挂载为只读。所有可写状态必须放在已声明的卷中。"

#: src/container/security.md:16 src/container/security.md:18
#: src/container/security.md:19 src/container/security.md:20
#: src/container/security.md:21
msgid "All backends"
msgstr "所有后端"

#: src/container/security.md:17
msgid ""
"Run privileged: grants ALL Linux capabilities + access to host devices. "
"**Avoid unless absolutely necessary.**"
msgstr "以特权模式运行：授予全部 Linux capabilities 及宿主设备访问权限。**除非绝对必要，否则请避免使用。**"

#: src/container/security.md:17
msgid ""
"Docker / Podman / Lima only — apple/container has no concept and **drops the"
" field** with a warning"
msgstr "仅适用于 Docker / Podman / Lima——apple/container 无对应概念，会**丢弃该字段**并输出警告"

#: src/container/security.md:18
msgid ""
"UID, username, or `\"UID:GID\"` — runs the container's processes as that "
"identity. The image's CMD ignores this if it does its own user-switching, "
"but most properly-built images respect it."
msgstr ""
"UID、用户名或 `\"UID:GID\"` ——以该身份运行容器进程。如果镜像的 CMD "
"自行切换用户，则此字段无效，但大多数规范构建的镜像都会遵守此设置。"

#: src/container/security.md:20
msgid ""
"Linux capabilities to add. Specific (e.g. `[\"NET_BIND_SERVICE\"]`), not "
"blanket."
msgstr "要添加的 Linux capabilities。应使用具体项（如 `[\"NET_BIND_SERVICE\"]`），而非全量添加。"

#: src/container/security.md:21
msgid ""
"Capabilities to drop. `[\"ALL\"]` is the canonical \"drop everything\" "
"starting point."
msgstr "要丢弃的 capabilities。`[\"ALL\"]` 是「丢弃全部」的规范起点。"

#: src/container/security.md:22
msgid ""
"Seccomp profile path or `\"default\"` (uses the runtime's default profile)."
msgstr "Seccomp 配置文件路径，或 `\"default\"`（使用运行时默认配置文件）。"

#: src/container/security.md:22
msgid ""
"Docker / Podman / Lima only — apple/container has no equivalent and **drops "
"the field** with a warning"
msgstr "仅适用于 Docker / Podman / Lima——apple/container 无对应机制，会**丢弃该字段**并输出警告"

#: src/container/security.md:24
msgid ""
"⚠️ **Cross-backend security caveat.** `privileged`, `seccomp`, `--security-"
"opt no-new-privileges`, IPC/PID namespace sharing, and SELinux mount labels "
"are **not honored on apple/container** — its Apple-VM model means those "
"concepts don't translate. Perry's normalization pass drops the fields and "
"emits a `tracing::warn!` rather than silently downgrading the security "
"policy. For production deployments that demand cross-backend parity, set "
"`EnforcementMode::Strict` on the engine — any unsupported security field "
"becomes a hard `up()` failure rather than a silent drop. Full matrix at "
"[Cross-Backend Determinism](./determinism.md)."
msgstr ""
"⚠️ **跨后端安全注意事项。** `privileged`、`seccomp`、`--security-opt no-new-"
"privileges`、IPC/PID 命名空间共享以及 SELinux 挂载标签在 **apple/container 上不生效**——其 Apple"
" VM 模型意味着这些概念无法映射。Perry 的规范化过程会丢弃这些字段并发出 `tracing::warn!` "
"警告，而不是静默降级安全策略。对于要求跨后端一致性的生产部署，请在引擎上设置 "
"`EnforcementMode::Strict`——任何不支持的安全字段都会导致 `up()` 硬失败，而不是静默丢弃。完整矩阵请见 "
"[跨后端确定性](./determinism.md)。"

#: src/container/security.md:35
msgid "Recommended baseline"
msgstr "推荐基线配置"

#: src/container/security.md:37
msgid ""
"Start with maximum isolation and add back only what the workload needs:"
msgstr "从最大隔离开始，仅按工作负载需要逐步放开："

#: src/container/security.md:61
msgid "Field-by-field rationale:"
msgstr "逐字段说明："

#: src/container/security.md:63
msgid ""
"`read_only: true` — even an exploit that lands code execution can't persist "
"to the image's filesystem. Anything mutable goes into a declared volume."
msgstr "`read_only: true` ——即使漏洞触发了代码执行，也无法持久化写入镜像文件系统。所有可变状态均放入已声明的卷。"

#: src/container/security.md:66
msgid ""
"`cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]` — removes Linux capabilities the workload didn't "
"explicitly ask for. Most apps need none."
msgstr ""
"`cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]` ——移除工作负载未显式申请的 Linux capabilities。大多数应用无需任何 "
"capability。"

#: src/container/security.md:68
msgid ""
"`user: \"nobody\"` — non-root inside the container. If the image doesn't "
"have a `nobody` user, replace with `\"65534:65534\"` (the numeric UID/GID of"
" `nobody` on most distros)."
msgstr ""
"`user: \"nobody\"` ——在容器内以非 root 身份运行。若镜像中没有 `nobody` 用户，请替换为 "
"`\"65534:65534\"`（大多数发行版中 `nobody` 的数字 UID/GID）。"

#: src/container/security.md:71
msgid ""
"`workdir: \"/tmp\"` — the only writable location under `read_only: true` is "
"`/tmp` (which is `tmpfs`\\-backed by default)."
msgstr ""
"`workdir: \"/tmp\"` ——在 `read_only: true` 下唯一可写的位置是 `/tmp`（默认由 `tmpfs` 支撑）。"

#: src/container/security.md:73
msgid ""
"`seccomp: \"default\"` — uses docker's default seccomp profile (~50 syscalls"
" blocked)."
msgstr "`seccomp: \"default\"` ——使用 Docker 的默认 seccomp 配置文件（约阻断 50 个系统调用）。"

#: src/container/security.md:76
msgid "Capability addition patterns"
msgstr "按需添加 capability 的模式"

#: src/container/security.md:78
msgid "`cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]` plus targeted `cap_add`:"
msgstr "`cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]` 搭配精准的 `cap_add`："

#: src/container/security.md:80
msgid "Workload"
msgstr "工作负载"

#: src/container/security.md:80
msgid "Capabilities"
msgstr "Capabilities"

#: src/container/security.md:82
msgid "**Web server binding to port 80/443**"
msgstr "**绑定 80/443 端口的 Web 服务器**"

#: src/container/security.md:82
msgid "`cap_add: [\"NET_BIND_SERVICE\"]`"
msgstr "`cap_add: [\"NET_BIND_SERVICE\"]`"

#: src/container/security.md:83
msgid "**Network namespace manipulation**"
msgstr "**网络命名空间操作**"

#: src/container/security.md:83
msgid "`cap_add: [\"NET_ADMIN\"]`"
msgstr "`cap_add: [\"NET_ADMIN\"]`"

#: src/container/security.md:84
msgid "**Kernel time setting**"
msgstr "**内核时间设置**"

#: src/container/security.md:84
msgid "`cap_add: [\"SYS_TIME\"]`"
msgstr "`cap_add: [\"SYS_TIME\"]`"

#: src/container/security.md:85
msgid "**chown** to other users (rare)"
msgstr "**chown 给其他用户（少见）**"

#: src/container/security.md:85
msgid "`cap_add: [\"CHOWN\"]`"
msgstr "`cap_add: [\"CHOWN\"]`"

#: src/container/security.md:86
msgid "**Bind-mount filesystems inside**"
msgstr "**在容器内绑定挂载文件系统**"

#: src/container/security.md:86
msgid "`cap_add: [\"SYS_ADMIN\"]` (still avoid if possible)"
msgstr "`cap_add: [\"SYS_ADMIN\"]`（仍应尽量避免）"

#: src/container/security.md:88
msgid ""
"The full capability list is in `man capabilities(7)`. Always start with "
"`cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]` and add only what fails when removed — most "
"applications need zero capabilities."
msgstr ""
"完整 capability 列表请参阅 `man capabilities(7)`。始终以 `cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]` "
"为起点，仅添加移除后会导致失败的项——大多数应用所需 capability 数量为零。"

#: src/container/security.md:92
msgid "Image verification"
msgstr "镜像验证"

#: src/container/security.md:94
msgid ""
"Set `PERRY_CONTAINER_VERIFY_IMAGES=1` to enable cosign keyless verification "
"on every `run()`, `create()`, and `pullImage()` call:"
msgstr ""
"设置 `PERRY_CONTAINER_VERIFY_IMAGES=1` 以对每次 `run()`、`create()` 和 `pullImage()`"
" 调用启用 cosign 无密钥验证："

#: src/container/security.md:102
msgid "Perry's verifier:"
msgstr "Perry 的验证器："

#: src/container/security.md:104
msgid "Resolves the image tag to its digest via `inspect_image`."
msgstr "通过 `inspect_image` 将镜像标签解析为其摘要。"

#: src/container/security.md:105
msgid ""
"Looks up the digest in an in-memory `VERIFICATION_CACHE` — subsequent runs "
"against the same digest are free."
msgstr "在内存中的 `VERIFICATION_CACHE` 中查找摘要——对同一摘要的后续运行不产生额外开销。"

#: src/container/security.md:107
msgid ""
"Runs `cosign verify --certificate-identity ${CHAINGUARD_IDENTITY} "
"--certificate-oidc-issuer ${CHAINGUARD_ISSUER} <ref>@<digest>` and caches "
"pass/fail."
msgstr ""
"运行 `cosign verify --certificate-identity ${CHAINGUARD_IDENTITY} "
"--certificate-oidc-issuer ${CHAINGUARD_ISSUER} <ref>@<digest>` 并缓存通过/失败结果。"

#: src/container/security.md:110
msgid ""
"On fail, the FFI rejects with a `verification failed` error (the container "
"is never created)."
msgstr "验证失败时，FFI 会以 `verification failed` 错误拒绝请求（容器不会被创建）。"

#: src/container/security.md:113
msgid "Default identity / issuer point at Chainguard's keyless signing flow:"
msgstr "默认的 identity / issuer 指向 Chainguard 的无密钥签名流程："

#: src/container/security.md:115
msgid "Const"
msgstr "常量"

#: src/container/security.md:117
msgid "`CHAINGUARD_IDENTITY`"
msgstr "`CHAINGUARD_IDENTITY`"

#: src/container/security.md:117
msgid ""
"`https://github.com/chainguard-"
"images/images/.github/workflows/sign.yaml@refs/heads/main`"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/security.md:118
msgid "`CHAINGUARD_ISSUER`"
msgstr "`CHAINGUARD_ISSUER`"

#: src/container/security.md:118
msgid "`https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com`"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/security.md:120
msgid ""
"For your own org's images, override these via the (planned) per-call "
"verification options. For now, using Chainguard-signed base images is the "
"path of least resistance — `cgr.dev/chainguard/<tool>` is signed."
msgstr ""
"对于您自己组织的镜像，可通过（计划中的）按调用验证选项进行覆盖。目前，使用 Chainguard "
"签名的基础镜像是阻力最小的方案——`cgr.dev/chainguard/<tool>` 已签名。"

#: src/container/security.md:124
msgid ""
"**Cosign required.** Set `PERRY_CONTAINER_VERIFY_IMAGES=1` only when "
"`cosign` is installed and on `PATH`. The verification is OFF by default so "
"the bare-metal `./my-app` execution doesn't depend on a separate cosign "
"install."
msgstr ""
"**需要安装 cosign。** 仅在 `cosign` 已安装且在 `PATH` 中时才设置 "
"`PERRY_CONTAINER_VERIFY_IMAGES=1`。默认情况下验证为关闭状态，以避免裸机执行 `./my-app` 时依赖额外的 "
"cosign 安装。"

#: src/container/security.md:129
msgid "Capability sandbox helper"
msgstr "能力沙箱辅助工具"

#: src/container/security.md:131
msgid ""
"For one-off command execution against an untrusted image (CI helper, build "
"tool, code-evaluation sandbox), use the [`run_capability` "
"pattern](./containers.md#hardened-single-container-run) which wraps `run()` "
"with the maximum-isolation defaults:"
msgstr ""
"对于针对不受信任镜像的一次性命令执行（CI 辅助工具、构建工具、代码评估沙箱），使用 [`run_capability` "
"模式](./containers.md#hardened-single-container-run)，它以最大隔离默认值封装 `run()`："

#: src/container/security.md:136
msgid "`read_only: true`"
msgstr "`read_only: true`"

#: src/container/security.md:137
msgid "`cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]`"
msgstr "`cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]`"

#: src/container/security.md:138
msgid "No network attached"
msgstr "不附加网络"

#: src/container/security.md:139
msgid "`user: \"nobody\"`"
msgstr "`user: \"nobody\"`"

#: src/container/security.md:140
msgid "Image verified via cosign before pull"
msgstr "通过 cosign 在拉取前验证镜像"

#: src/container/security.md:142
msgid ""
"This is the same path the internal `perry-stdlib::container::capability` "
"module uses for shell-command sandboxing in plugin systems."
msgstr ""
"这与内部 `perry-stdlib::container::capability` 模块在插件系统中用于 shell 命令沙箱化的路径相同。"

#: src/container/security.md:145
msgid "Workload-graph policy tiers (`perry/workloads`)"
msgstr "工作负载图策略层级（`perry/workloads`）"

#: src/container/security.md:147
msgid ""
"For multi-node deployments where different workloads have different trust "
"levels, the workload-graph engine accepts a per-node `policy`:"
msgstr "对于不同工作负载具有不同信任级别的多节点部署，工作负载图引擎接受每个节点的 `policy`："

#: src/container/security.md:150
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { graph, runGraph, runtime, policy } from \"perry/workloads\";\n"
"\n"
"const g = graph(\"my-app\", {\n"
"  trusted_db:    { image: \"postgres:16-alpine\",\n"
"                   runtime: runtime.oci(),\n"
"                   policy:  policy.default() },        // no extra hardening\n"
"\n"
"  isolated_api:  { image: \"myapp/api\",\n"
"                   runtime: runtime.oci(),\n"
"                   policy:  policy.isolated() },       // no_network=true\n"
"\n"
"  hardened_proxy: { image: \"myapp/proxy\",\n"
"                    runtime: runtime.oci(),\n"
"                    policy:  policy.hardened() },      // read_only_root + seccomp\n"
"\n"
"  untrusted_eval: { image: \"myapp/sandbox\",\n"
"                    runtime: runtime.microvm(),         // ← required by tier\n"
"                    policy:  policy.untrusted() },     // microVM-only, all hardening on\n"
"});\n"
"\n"
"await runGraph(g);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/security.md:174
msgid "The four `PolicyTier` levels and what they enforce:"
msgstr "四个 `PolicyTier` 级别及其强制执行的内容："

#: src/container/security.md:176
msgid "`no_network`"
msgstr "`no_network`"

#: src/container/security.md:176
msgid "`read_only_root`"
msgstr "`read_only_root`"

#: src/container/security.md:176
msgid "`microvm`"
msgstr "`microvm`"

#: src/container/security.md:178
msgid "`default()`"
msgstr "`default()`"

#: src/container/security.md:179
msgid "`isolated()`"
msgstr "`isolated()`"

#: src/container/security.md:179 src/container/security.md:180
#: src/container/security.md:181
msgid "✅"
msgstr "✅"

#: src/container/security.md:180
msgid "`hardened()`"
msgstr "`hardened()`"

#: src/container/security.md:181
msgid "`untrusted()`"
msgstr "`untrusted()`"

#: src/container/security.md:181
msgid "**required**"
msgstr "**必需**"

#: src/container/security.md:183
msgid ""
"`untrusted` requires kernel-level isolation (i.e. a microVM, not a shared-"
"kernel container). When the active backend doesn't expose a microVM runtime "
"(`apple/container`'s VM mode, Lima, Firecracker), the engine returns "
"`BackendNotAvailable` rather than silently dropping the isolation guarantee."
" Use `PERRY_ALLOW_UNTRUSTED_SHARED_KERNEL=1` to opt out — **not recommended "
"for actually-untrusted code.**"
msgstr ""
"`untrusted` 需要内核级隔离（即 microVM，而非共享内核容器）。当活跃后端未提供 microVM "
"运行时（`apple/container` 的 VM 模式、Lima、Firecracker），引擎将返回 "
"`BackendNotAvailable`，而不是静默地放弃隔离保证。使用 "
"`PERRY_ALLOW_UNTRUSTED_SHARED_KERNEL=1` 选择退出——**不建议用于实际不受信任的代码。**"

#: src/container/security.md:190
msgid ""
"User-explicit per-flag overrides on top of a tier are honored: setting "
"`policy.tier = \"default\"` and `no_network: true` produces an isolated-"
"network default-tier node."
msgstr ""
"在层级之上，用户显式的逐标志覆盖会被遵守：将 `policy.tier = \"default\"` 与 `no_network: true` "
"一起设置，将生成一个隔离网络的默认层级节点。"

#: src/container/security.md:194
msgid "Defense in depth"
msgstr "纵深防御"

#: src/container/security.md:196
msgid "Stacking patterns for production:"
msgstr "生产环境的叠加模式："

#: src/container/security.md:198
msgid "**Verify images** (`PERRY_CONTAINER_VERIFY_IMAGES=1`)."
msgstr "**验证镜像**（`PERRY_CONTAINER_VERIFY_IMAGES=1`）。"

#: src/container/security.md:199
msgid "**Run as non-root** (`user: \"nobody\"` or numeric UID)."
msgstr "**以非 root 用户运行**（`user: \"nobody\"` 或数字 UID）。"

#: src/container/security.md:200
msgid ""
"**Drop all capabilities, add specific ones back** (`cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]` + "
"minimal `cap_add`)."
msgstr "**删除所有能力，按需添加特定能力**（`cap_drop: [\"ALL\"]` + 最小化 `cap_add`）。"

#: src/container/security.md:202
msgid "**Read-only root filesystem** (`read_only: true`)."
msgstr "**只读根文件系统**（`read_only: true`）。"

#: src/container/security.md:203
msgid ""
"**Internal networks for the database side** (`internal: true` on the db's "
"network — see [Networking](./networking.md#internal-only-networks-internal-"
"true))."
msgstr ""
"**数据库侧使用内部网络**（在 db 的网络上设置 `internal: "
"true`——参见[网络](./networking.md#internal-only-networks-internal-true)）。"

#: src/container/security.md:205
msgid ""
"**No published ports for private services** (omit `ports:` on internal-only "
"services)."
msgstr "**私有服务不发布端口**（内部专用服务省略 `ports:`）。"

#: src/container/security.md:207
msgid "**Resource limits** (planned: `mem_limit`, `cpu_limit` on Service)."
msgstr "**资源限制**（计划中：Service 上的 `mem_limit`、`cpu_limit`）。"

#: src/container/security.md:211
msgid ""
"[Compose orchestration](./compose.md) — applying these knobs in a stack "
"spec."
msgstr "[Compose 编排](./compose.md)——在堆栈规范中应用这些配置项。"

#: src/container/security.md:213
msgid ""
"[Production patterns](./production-patterns.md) — Forgejo example uses "
"several of these (internal-only db net, published web port, USER_UID/GID)."
msgstr ""
"[生产模式](./production-patterns.md)——Forgejo 示例使用了其中多项（仅内部 db 网络、发布 web "
"端口、USER_UID/GID）。"

#: src/container/security.md:216
msgid ""
"[Networking](./networking.md) — internal-only networks for database "
"isolation."
msgstr "[网络](./networking.md)——用于数据库隔离的内部专用网络。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:3
msgid ""
"This page is a guided tour of [`example-code/forgejo-"
"deployment`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/tree/main/example-"
"code/forgejo-deployment), a working production-quality deployment of "
"[Forgejo](https://forgejo.org/) (self-hosted Git) using the real Forgejo "
"image from the official `data.forgejo.org` registry. The example was driven "
"end-to-end against live Docker; the patterns here are what survived."
msgstr ""
"本页面是对 [`example-code/forgejo-"
"deployment`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/tree/main/example-"
"code/forgejo-deployment) 的导览，这是一个使用来自官方 `data.forgejo.org` 仓库的真实 Forgejo "
"镜像，通过 Perry 部署 [Forgejo](https://forgejo.org/)（自托管 Git）的生产质量工作示例。该示例已针对实时 "
"Docker 进行了端到端验证；此处记录的是经过实践验证的模式。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:9
msgid ""
"The full source is at [`example-code/forgejo-"
"deployment/main.ts`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/tree/main/example-"
"code/forgejo-deployment/main.ts). This page documents the _patterns_, not "
"every line."
msgstr ""
"完整源码位于 [`example-code/forgejo-"
"deployment/main.ts`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/tree/main/example-"
"code/forgejo-deployment/main.ts)。本页记录的是_模式_，而非每一行代码。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:12
msgid "Lifecycle: `up + verify + exit 0` then a separate `--down`"
msgstr "生命周期：`up + verify + exit 0`，然后单独执行 `--down`"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:14
msgid ""
"Perry's runtime currently does not deliver `process.on('SIGINT', ...)` to "
"your TS code. So the canonical \"Ctrl-C tears down the stack\" pattern isn't"
" writable today. Instead, follow the `docker compose up -d` / `docker "
"compose down` model: deploy + verify + exit 0, with teardown behind a "
"separate `--down` invocation:"
msgstr ""
"Perry 的运行时目前不会将 `process.on('SIGINT', ...)` 传递给你的 TypeScript 代码。因此，\"Ctrl-C "
"拆除堆栈\"这一经典模式目前无法实现。应遵循 `docker compose up -d` / `docker compose down` 模型：部署 "
"+ 验证 + exit 0，通过单独的 `--down` 调用进行拆除："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:20
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"async function main() {\n"
"  const args = process.argv.slice(2);\n"
"  const config = buildConfig();\n"
"  if (args.includes(\"--down\")) {\n"
"    await cmdDown(config);\n"
"  } else {\n"
"    await cmdUp(config);\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:32
msgid "The example's `cmdUp`:"
msgstr "示例中的 `cmdUp`："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:34
msgid "Pre-flight backend probe + port-conflict guard."
msgstr "预检后端探测 + 端口冲突检查。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:35
msgid "Call `up()` with the canonical spec."
msgstr "使用规范规范调用 `up()`。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:36
msgid ""
"Poll readiness probes (postgres `pg_isready`, then forgejo `/api/healthz`)."
msgstr "轮询就绪探针（postgres 的 `pg_isready`，然后是 forgejo 的 `/api/healthz`）。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:38
msgid "Print an operator-facing banner with URLs + \"how to tear down\"."
msgstr "打印面向运维人员的横幅，包含 URL 及\"如何拆除\"说明。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:39
msgid "Exit 0. Containers keep running thanks to `restart: unless-stopped`."
msgstr "退出 0。容器因 `restart: unless-stopped` 而持续运行。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:42
msgid "The example's `cmdDown`:"
msgstr "示例中的 `cmdDown`："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:44
msgid ""
"Re-call `up()` with the same spec — idempotent: services already running are"
" detected and skipped, returning the same handle the original deploy got."
msgstr "使用相同规范重新调用 `up()`——幂等：已运行的服务将被检测并跳过，返回与原始部署相同的句柄。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:47
msgid ""
"Call `down(handle, { volumes: destroy })`. `destroy` is set from "
"`FORGEJO_DESTROY_ON_EXIT=1`."
msgstr ""
"调用 `down(handle, { volumes: destroy })`。`destroy` 由 "
"`FORGEJO_DESTROY_ON_EXIT=1` 设置。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:50
msgid "Two-network split: internal db + public web"
msgstr "双网络分割：内部 db + 公共 web"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:52
msgid ""
"The Forgejo example puts postgres on an internal-only network and forgejo on"
" both that network and a public bridge:"
msgstr "Forgejo 示例将 postgres 放置在仅内部网络上，并将 forgejo 同时连接到该网络和公共桥接网络："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:55
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"networks: {\n"
"  \"forgejo-db-net\":  { driver: \"bridge\", internal: true }, // postgres unreachable from host\n"
"  \"forgejo-web-net\": { driver: \"bridge\" },                 // forgejo's web + SSH ports\n"
"},\n"
"services: {\n"
"  db: {\n"
"    networks: [\"forgejo-db-net\"],\n"
"    // no `ports:` — postgres is invisible to the host\n"
"  },\n"
"  forgejo: {\n"
"    networks: [\"forgejo-db-net\", \"forgejo-web-net\"],\n"
"    ports: [\"3000:3000\", \"2222:22\"],  // public web + SSH\n"
"  },\n"
"},\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:72
msgid ""
"Why: postgres should never be reachable from the host (or from sibling "
"stacks), but forgejo needs both inbound HTTP from the host AND outbound DB "
"queries to postgres. Two networks is the cleanest expression of that split."
msgstr ""
"原因：postgres 不应从主机（或相邻堆栈）访问，但 forgejo 既需要从主机接收入站 HTTP，又需要向 postgres 发出出站 DB "
"查询。两个网络是表达这种分割的最简洁方式。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:77
msgid "Stable container names for cross-service DNS"
msgstr "用于跨服务 DNS 的稳定容器名称"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:79
msgid ""
"Perry's compose engine creates each container with a `{md5}-{random}` "
"derived name and doesn't yet register the service KEY (`db`, `forgejo`) as a"
" network alias. So `FORGEJO__database__HOST: 'db:5432'` would fail name "
"resolution at runtime. The Forgejo example pins explicit `container_name` "
"values:"
msgstr ""
"Perry 的 compose 引擎以 `{md5}-{random}` "
"派生名称创建每个容器，且尚未将服务键（`db`、`forgejo`）注册为网络别名。因此，`FORGEJO__database__HOST: "
"'db:5432'` 在运行时会导致名称解析失败。Forgejo 示例通过固定显式的 `container_name` 值来解决此问题："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:85
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const dbHostname      = \"forgejo-db\";\n"
"const forgejoHostname = \"forgejo-app\";\n"
"\n"
"services: {\n"
"  db: {\n"
"    image: `postgres:${pgVersion}`,\n"
"    container_name: dbHostname,                  // ← stable target\n"
"    // …\n"
"  },\n"
"  forgejo: {\n"
"    image: `data.forgejo.org/forgejo/forgejo:${version}`,\n"
"    container_name: forgejoHostname,\n"
"    environment: {\n"
"      FORGEJO__database__HOST: `${dbHostname}:5432`,  // ← refers to it\n"
"      // …\n"
"    },\n"
"  },\n"
"},\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:106
msgid ""
"See [Networking → Cross-service DNS](./networking.md#cross-service-dns) for "
"the full backstory and why this is the workaround until service-key network-"
"alias support lands."
msgstr ""
"请参阅[网络 → 跨服务 DNS](./networking.md#cross-service-"
"dns)，了解完整背景以及为何这是在服务键网络别名支持落地之前的变通方案。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:110
msgid "OpenSSH on :22 + `START_SSH_SERVER=false`"
msgstr "OpenSSH 监听 :22 + `START_SSH_SERVER=false`"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:112
msgid ""
"Forgejo's official image runs `/usr/sbin/sshd` on container port 22 in its "
"entrypoint script, then runs the forgejo binary. If you also set "
"`FORGEJO__server__START_SSH_SERVER=true`, forgejo's Go-based built-in SSH "
"server tries to bind :22 too — and the container exit-0's with \"bind: "
"address already in use\"."
msgstr ""
"Forgejo 的官方镜像会在其入口脚本中于容器端口 22 上运行 `/usr/sbin/sshd`，然后再运行 forgejo "
"二进制文件。如果同时设置了 `FORGEJO__server__START_SSH_SERVER=true`，forgejo 基于 Go 的内置 SSH"
" 服务器也会尝试绑定 :22 —— 容器将以退出码 0 退出，并提示 \"bind: address already in use\"。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:118
msgid ""
"The standard Forgejo deployment pattern is to **let OpenSSH handle SSH on "
":22 and tell forgejo not to start its own**:"
msgstr ""
"标准的 Forgejo 部署模式是**让 OpenSSH 在 :22 上处理 SSH，并告知 forgejo 不要启动自己的 SSH 服务**："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:121
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"environment: {\n"
"  FORGEJO__server__START_SSH_SERVER: \"false\",   // ← critical\n"
"  FORGEJO__server__SSH_PORT:         \"2222\",    // public host port\n"
"  FORGEJO__server__SSH_LISTEN_PORT:  \"22\",      // container-internal port\n"
"  // …\n"
"},\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:130
msgid ""
"Forgejo writes git users' authorized_keys to `/data/git/.ssh/`, which the "
"in-container OpenSSH consumes. Git operations route through sshd on :22, "
"then forgejo's `gitea-shell` script."
msgstr ""
"Forgejo 将 git 用户的 authorized_keys 写入 `/data/git/.ssh/`，容器内的 OpenSSH "
"会读取该文件。Git 操作通过 :22 上的 sshd 路由，然后经由 forgejo 的 `gitea-shell` 脚本处理。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:134
msgid "Healthcheck-gated dependency startup"
msgstr "基于健康检查的依赖启动顺序"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:136
msgid ""
"postgres takes ~5–10 seconds to initialise on first run (initdb + listener "
"bind). Without gating, forgejo starts immediately, can't connect, and burns "
"retry budget. The fix is a per-service `healthcheck` plus `depends_on: { "
"svc: { condition: 'service_healthy' } }`:"
msgstr ""
"postgres 在首次运行时（initdb + 监听器绑定）需要约 5–10 秒完成初始化。若不进行顺序控制，forgejo "
"会立即启动，因无法连接而耗尽重试次数。解决方法是为每个服务配置 `healthcheck`，并设置 `depends_on: { svc: { "
"condition: 'service_healthy' } }`："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:142
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"db: {\n"
"  image: \"postgres:16-alpine\",\n"
"  // …\n"
"  healthcheck: {\n"
"    test: [\"CMD-SHELL\", \"pg_isready -U forgejo -d forgejo\"],\n"
"    interval: \"5s\",\n"
"    timeout: \"3s\",\n"
"    retries: 10,\n"
"    start_period: \"30s\",\n"
"  },\n"
"},\n"
"forgejo: {\n"
"  // …\n"
"  depends_on: { db: { condition: \"service_healthy\" } },\n"
"},\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:160
msgid ""
"Even with that, the example _also_ runs an explicit readiness loop "
"post-`up()` for the full HTTP `/api/healthz` path — the healthcheck gates "
"**container startup** but the operator banner shouldn't print until the API "
"is _serving_:"
msgstr ""
"即便如此，示例中还在 `up()` 之后额外运行了一个显式的就绪等待循环，用于检测完整的 HTTP `/api/healthz` 路径 —— "
"健康检查控制的是**容器启动**，但在 API 真正**开始提供服务**之前，操作提示横幅不应打印："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:165
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"async function waitForForgejo(stack: number, timeoutMs: number): Promise<boolean> {\n"
"  const deadline = Date.now() + timeoutMs;\n"
"  while (Date.now() < deadline) {\n"
"    try {\n"
"      // Probe from INSIDE the forgejo container so the docker-proxy\n"
"      // bind-up window doesn't trip the host-side curl.\n"
"      await exec(stack, \"forgejo\", [\n"
"        \"wget\", \"-q\", \"-O\", \"/dev/null\",\n"
"        \"--timeout=2\", \"--tries=1\",\n"
"        \"http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/healthz\",\n"
"      ]);\n"
"      return true;\n"
"    } catch (_e) {\n"
"      await new Promise((r) => setTimeout(r, 2000));\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"  return false;\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:186
msgid ""
"`/api/healthz` is Forgejo's no-auth liveness endpoint that returns 200 once "
"the web server is up AND the database / cache subsystems pinged "
"successfully. Don't use `/api/v1/version` — when `REQUIRE_SIGNIN_VIEW=true` "
"(a production-hardening default) it returns 401, and `wget` exits non-zero "
"on HTTP error responses."
msgstr ""
"`/api/healthz` 是 Forgejo 的无需鉴权的存活检测端点，当 Web 服务器启动且数据库/缓存子系统均成功 ping 通后返回 "
"200。不要使用 `/api/v1/version` —— 当 "
"`REQUIRE_SIGNIN_VIEW=true`（生产环境加固的默认值）时，该端点返回 401，而 `wget` 在收到 HTTP "
"错误响应时会以非零状态退出。"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:192
msgid "Stable secrets for redeploy"
msgstr "用于重新部署的稳定密钥"

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:194
msgid ""
"The Forgejo example's `buildConfig()` uses **truthy-fallback** semantics for"
" env vars (`process.env[name] || fallback`) because Perry's "
"`process.env[NONEXISTENT]` returns an empty-ish value where strict equality "
"to `undefined` / `''` doesn't hold:"
msgstr ""
"Forgejo 示例的 `buildConfig()` 对环境变量使用**真值回退**语义（`process.env[name] || "
"fallback`），原因是 Perry 的 `process.env[NONEXISTENT]` 返回一个类空值，严格相等于 `undefined` "
"/ `''` 的判断并不成立："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:205
msgid "The defaults for the three secret-bearing fields are random hex:"
msgstr "三个包含密钥的字段的默认值为随机十六进制字符串："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:213
msgid ""
"This is fine for **first-run** / dev / smoke-test, but **breaks any "
"subsequent run against the same volumes** because:"
msgstr "这对于**首次运行** / 开发 / 冒烟测试没有问题，但**对同一数据卷的后续运行会失败**，原因如下："

#: src/container/production-patterns.md:216
msgid ""
"Postgres rows were authored under the prior password — new password rejects "
"the connection."
msgstr "Postgres 中的数据行是使用旧密码写入的 —— 新密码将导致连接被拒绝。"

