"PipeWire / ALSA，Windows 上使用 WASAPI / DirectSound / WinMM，Android 上使用 "
"AAudio（API 26+）/ OpenSL ES——运行时自动选择。"

#: src/system/audio_module.md:138
msgid "Web autoplay policy"
msgstr "Web 自动播放策略"

#: src/system/audio_module.md:140
msgid ""
"Browsers don't allow audio playback before a user gesture. The "
"`AudioContext` is lazily created on the first `loadSound()` / `play()` call;"
" if that call happens **before** any user interaction, the context starts in"
" a suspended state and your `play()` is queued. Trigger a user-interaction-"
"bound `resumeAll()` (or just any other `play()` inside a click handler) to "
"release it."
msgstr ""
"浏览器不允许在用户手势发生之前播放音频。`AudioContext` 会在首次调用 `loadSound()` / `play()` "
"时惰性创建；若该调用发生在任何用户交互**之前**，上下文将以挂起状态启动，且 `play()` 会被排队。请在用户交互绑定的回调中触发 "
"`resumeAll()`（或在点击处理程序中调用任意 `play()`）来解除挂起。"

