#: src/system/media.md:97
msgid ""
"Stub platforms link cleanly against the same FFI surface — code that imports"
" `perry/media` compiles on every target. `createPlayer` returns `0` on a "
"stub backend so `if (player === 0)` is the canonical \"feature not available"
" here\" check."
msgstr ""
"桩平台与同一 FFI 接口干净链接 —— 导入 `perry/media` 的代码可在所有目标上编译。在桩后端上 `createPlayer` 返回 "
"`0`，因此 `if (player === 0)` 是判断「此处不可用此特性」的规范方式。"

#: src/system/media.md:102
msgid ""
"On Linux, `setNowPlaying` exposes the player to the desktop via MPRIS "
"(`org.mpris.MediaPlayer2.perry-<pid>` on the session bus). GNOME Shell, KDE "
"Plasma, `playerctl`, and any Bluetooth-headphone media-key bridge that "
"speaks MPRIS will see the metadata and route Play / Pause / PlayPause / Stop"
" / Seek / SetPosition back to the player. The MPRIS server is lazy-"
"bootstrapped on the first `setNowPlaying` call so apps that don't need lock-"
"screen integration don't pay the zbus startup cost. `Next` / `Previous` are "
"no-ops (single-track playback model); playlists are an app-level concern."
msgstr ""
"在 Linux 上，`setNowPlaying` 通过 MPRIS（会话总线上的 "
"`org.mpris.MediaPlayer2.perry-<pid>`）将播放器暴露给桌面。GNOME Shell、KDE "
"Plasma、`playerctl`，以及任何使用 MPRIS 的蓝牙耳机媒体键桥接都可以看到元数据，并将 Play / Pause / "
"PlayPause / Stop / Seek / SetPosition 路由回播放器。MPRIS 服务器会在首次调用 `setNowPlaying`"
" 时延迟启动，因此不需要锁屏集成的应用无需承担 zbus 启动成本。`Next` / `Previous` "
"是空操作（单曲播放模型）；播放列表是应用级关注点。"

#: src/system/media.md:112
msgid "Android — background playback"
msgstr "Android —— 后台播放"

#: src/system/media.md:114
msgid ""
"Perry's Android backend wires `MediaSessionCompat` so the lock-screen tile, "
"Bluetooth headset, Android Auto, and Wear OS see the metadata pushed by "
"`setNowPlaying` and route headphone play/pause/stop/seek events back into "
"the registered `onStateChange` closure. That covers foreground use. Apps "
"that want playback to survive the activity being backgrounded (a podcast "
"app, music player, etc.) need a foreground service of their own — Android "
"will otherwise kill the audio when the process drops to the cached state. "
"Add the following to your app's `AndroidManifest.xml` and start the service "
"when playback begins:"
msgstr ""
"Perry 的 Android 后端连接了 `MediaSessionCompat`，因此锁屏磁贴、蓝牙耳机、Android Auto 和 Wear "
"OS 都可以看到通过 `setNowPlaying` 推送的元数据，并将耳机播放/暂停/停止/跳转事件路由回已注册的 `onStateChange` "
"闭包。这覆盖了前台用法。希望在 Activity 进入后台时也能继续播放的应用（播客应用、音乐播放器等）需要自己提供前台服务 —— "
"否则当进程进入缓存状态时，Android 会终止音频。在你的应用 `AndroidManifest.xml` 中添加以下内容，并在播放开始时启动该服务："

#: src/system/media.md:126
msgid "\".PerryMediaService\""
msgstr "\".PerryMediaService\""

#: src/system/media.md:127
msgid "\"mediaPlayback\""
msgstr "\"mediaPlayback\""

#: src/system/media.md:128
msgid "\"false\""
msgstr "\"false\""

#: src/system/media.md:129
msgid "\"android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE\""
msgstr "\"android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE\""

#: src/system/media.md:130
msgid "\"android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE_MEDIA_PLAYBACK\""
msgstr "\"android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE_MEDIA_PLAYBACK\""

#: src/system/media.md:133
msgid ""
"The service implementation is app-specific — it should hold a "
"`MediaSessionCompat.Token` (the same session Perry created), build a "
"`Notification.MediaStyle` notification from it, and call "
"`startForeground(...)` on `play` / `stopForeground(false)` on `pause` / "
"`stopSelf()` on `stop`. We deliberately don't ship a default service because"
" the notification's branding (small icon, tint, content intent) depends on "
"the host app."
msgstr ""
"服务实现是应用相关的 —— 它应持有一个 `MediaSessionCompat.Token`（与 Perry 创建的会话相同），从中构建 "
"`Notification.MediaStyle` 通知，并在 `play` 时调用 `startForeground(...)`、在 `pause` "
"时调用 `stopForeground(false)`、在 `stop` 时调用 "
"`stopSelf()`。我们刻意不提供默认服务，因为通知的品牌（小图标、染色、内容意图）取决于宿主应用。"

#: src/system/media.md:141
msgid "Threading notes"
msgstr "线程注意事项"

#: src/system/media.md:143
msgid ""
"The `onStateChange` and `onTimeUpdate` callbacks fire from the platform's "
"main UI thread on every backend, so they share the same JS heap as the "
"calling code. Implementation detail varies:"
msgstr ""
"`onStateChange` 和 `onTimeUpdate` 回调在每个后端上都从平台主 UI 线程触发，因此它们与调用代码共享相同的 JS "
"堆。实现细节因平台而异："

#: src/system/media.md:147
msgid ""
"**macOS / iOS / tvOS / visionOS** — driven by an `NSTimer` scheduled on the "
"main run loop at 10 Hz."
msgstr ""
"**macOS / iOS / tvOS / visionOS** —— 由调度在主运行循环上以 10 Hz 运行的 `NSTimer` 驱动。"

#: src/system/media.md:149
msgid ""
"**Android** — driven from `Java_com_perry_app_PerryBridge_nativePumpTick` "
"(the existing 125 Hz UI-thread pump), throttled internally to ~10 Hz. The "
"`prepare()` call runs on a background worker thread to avoid blocking the UI"
" on network buffering."
msgstr ""
"**Android** —— 从 `Java_com_perry_app_PerryBridge_nativePumpTick`（已有的 125 Hz "
"UI 线程泵）驱动，内部限流到约 10 Hz。`prepare()` 调用在后台工作线程上运行，以避免在网络缓冲时阻塞 UI。"

#: src/system/media.md:153
msgid ""
"**GTK4** — driven by a `glib::timeout_add_local` timer on the GLib main "
"loop. EOS / error messages arrive on the GStreamer bus and get forwarded to "
"per-player atomic flags via a `bus.add_watch_local` closure."
msgstr ""
"**GTK4** —— 由 GLib 主循环上的 `glib::timeout_add_local` 定时器驱动。EOS / 错误消息从 "
"GStreamer 总线到达，并通过 `bus.add_watch_local` 闭包转发到每个播放器的原子标志。"

#: src/system/media.md:157
msgid ""
"**Windows** — driven from the `GetMessageW` / `PeekMessageW` message loop "
"after each dispatch, throttled to 100 ms by wall-clock comparison."
msgstr ""
"**Windows** —— 由 `GetMessageW` / `PeekMessageW` 消息循环在每次 dispatch "
"后驱动，按墙钟时间比较限流到 100 ms。"

#: src/system/media.md:159
msgid ""
"**HarmonyOS** — Perry's `.so` cannot reach `@ohos.multimedia.media` "
"directly, so `perry/media` calls record intents into Mutex-protected drain "
"queues in `perry-runtime::media_playback`. The harvested `pages/Index.ets` "
"(emitted by `perry-codegen-arkts` whenever the module uses `perry/media`) "
"installs a 100 ms `setInterval` pump in `aboutToAppear` that drains the "
"queues, dispatches each op against the matching `media.AVPlayer` instance "
"(allocated lazily on the first `createPlayer` drain), and pushes state "
"observations back into the runtime via the `pushMediaState(handle, state, "
"current, duration)` NAPI export. AVPlayer's own `stateChange` / `timeUpdate`"
" / `error` / `endOfStream` events feed the same callback path. The pump runs"
" on the ArkTS UI thread, so closures fired by "
"`media_playback::push_media_state` share the same arena as Perry's `main()`."
" Lock-screen integration (`@ohos.multimedia.avsession`) is a follow-up — the"
" runtime queues now-playing metadata via `drainNowPlaying` but the ArkTS-"
"side AVSession dispatch is a no-op beyond a hilog line for now (tracked "
"under issue #369)."
msgstr ""
"**HarmonyOS** —— Perry 的 `.so` 无法直接访问 `@ohos.multimedia.media`，因此 "
"`perry/media` 调用会将意图记录到 `perry-runtime::media_playback` 中由 Mutex "
"保护的排空队列。每当模块使用 `perry/media` 时，由 `perry-codegen-arkts` 生成的 `pages/Index.ets`"
" 会在 `aboutToAppear` 中安装一个 100 ms `setInterval` 泵，用于排空队列、对相应的 "
"`media.AVPlayer` 实例（在首次 `createPlayer` 排空时延迟分配）分发各操作，并通过 "
"`pushMediaState(handle, state, current, duration)` NAPI "
"导出将状态观察推回运行时。AVPlayer 自身的 `stateChange` / `timeUpdate` / `error` / "
"`endOfStream` 事件也会喂入相同的回调路径。该泵在 ArkTS UI 线程上运行，因此 "
"`media_playback::push_media_state` 触发的闭包与 Perry 的 `main()` 共享同一个 "
"arena。锁屏集成（`@ohos.multimedia.avsession`）属于后续工作 —— 运行时现在通过 `drainNowPlaying` "
"排队 Now Playing 元数据，但 ArkTS 侧的 AVSession 分发目前只是一个 hilog 行的空操作（在 issue #369 "
"中跟踪）。"

#: src/system/media.md:177
msgid "Now Playing on Apple platforms"
msgstr "Apple 平台上的 Now Playing"

#: src/system/media.md:179
msgid ""
"Apple's MPNowPlayingInfoCenter is a process-wide singleton — the most recent"
" `setNowPlaying` call wins. For a single-player app (Subsonic client, "
"podcast player) this matches user expectation. The MPRemoteCommandCenter "
"handlers route `play` / `pause` / `togglePlayPause` events to the **first "
"live player handle** — multi-player apps that need an explicit \"active "
"player\" should manage that themselves."
msgstr ""
"Apple 的 MPNowPlayingInfoCenter 是一个进程级单例 —— 最近一次 `setNowPlaying` "
"调用胜出。对于单播放器应用（Subsonic 客户端、播客播放器）这符合用户预期。MPRemoteCommandCenter 处理器将 `play` /"
" `pause` / `togglePlayPause` 事件路由到**第一个存活的播放器句柄** —— "
"需要明确指定「活动播放器」的多播放器应用应自行管理。"

#: src/system/media.md:186
msgid "`artworkUrl` accepts:"
msgstr "`artworkUrl` 接受："

#: src/system/media.md:188
msgid "`file://` paths — loaded synchronously via NSImage / UIImage"
msgstr "`file://` 路径 —— 通过 NSImage / UIImage 同步加载"

#: src/system/media.md:189
msgid ""
"`https://` URLs — fetched synchronously via NSData(contentsOf:) and wrapped "
"in UIImage. The synchronous fetch is acceptable for a one-off artwork load "
"(the MPNowPlayingInfoCenter dict is consumed synchronously when set)."
msgstr ""
"`https://` URL —— 通过 NSData(contentsOf:) 同步获取并包装为 "
"UIImage。对于一次性封面加载来说同步获取是可接受的（MPNowPlayingInfoCenter 字典在设置时被同步消费）。"

#: src/system/media.md:194
msgid "watchOS Info.plist requirements"
msgstr "watchOS Info.plist 要求"

#: src/system/media.md:196
msgid ""
"watchOS keeps the audio engine alive when the watch screen sleeps **only "
"if** the app's `Info.plist` declares the `audio` background mode under "
"`WKBackgroundModes` (the WatchKit equivalent of iOS's `UIBackgroundModes`):"
msgstr ""
"**仅当**应用的 `Info.plist` 在 `WKBackgroundModes`（iOS `UIBackgroundModes` 在 "
"WatchKit 中的对应项）下声明 `audio` 后台模式时，watchOS 才会在表盘屏幕休眠时保持音频引擎存活："

#: src/system/media.md:207
msgid ""
"Without this entry the OS suspends the watch app a few seconds after the "
"wrist-down gesture or screen timeout, regardless of whether AVPlayer is "
"actively rendering. The runtime also auto-activates an `AVAudioSession` with"
" category `Playback` on the first `createPlayer(...)` call — combined with "
"the Info.plist entry, this is what tells watchOS the app intends to keep "
"playing audio in the background."
msgstr ""
"若没有此条目，无论 AVPlayer 是否正在主动渲染，操作系统都会在手腕放下手势或屏幕超时后几秒内挂起手表应用。运行时还会在首次 "
"`createPlayer(...)` 调用时自动以 `Playback` 类别激活一个 `AVAudioSession` —— 与 "
"Info.plist 条目结合使用，这就是告知 watchOS 应用打算在后台继续播放音频的方式。"

#: src/system/media.md:214
msgid ""
"The Now Playing surface on the watch face is independent from the paired "
"iPhone's lock screen — they're separate processes with separate "
"`MPNowPlayingInfoCenter` instances. `setNowPlaying` on watchOS targets the "
"watch's Now Playing complication / glance screen."
msgstr ""
"手表表盘上的 Now Playing 界面与配对 iPhone 的锁屏是独立的 —— 它们是带有独立 `MPNowPlayingInfoCenter` "
"实例的不同进程。watchOS 上的 `setNowPlaying` 针对手表的 Now Playing 复杂功能 / 概览屏幕。"

#: src/system/media.md:219
msgid "Subsonic example"
msgstr "Subsonic 示例"

#: src/system/media.md:221
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { createPlayer, play, setNowPlaying, onStateChange } from \"perry/media\";\n"
"\n"
"function streamUrl(serverUrl: string, user: string, pass: string, songId: string): string {\n"
"  const params = new URLSearchParams({\n"
"    u: user, p: pass, v: \"1.16.1\", c: \"PerryClient\", id: songId, format: \"mp3\",\n"
"  });\n"
"  return `${serverUrl}/rest/stream?${params.toString()}`;\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"const player = createPlayer(streamUrl(\"https://music.example.com\", \"alice\", \"secret\", \"12345\"));\n"
"setNowPlaying(player, \"All These Things That I've Done\", \"The Killers\", \"Hot Fuss\",\n"
"              \"https://music.example.com/rest/getCoverArt?id=12345&u=alice&p=secret&v=1.16.1&c=PerryClient\");\n"
"onStateChange(player, (state) => {\n"
"  if (state === \"ended\") {\n"
"    // queue.next() ...\n"
"  }\n"
"});\n"
"play(player);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/system/media.md:242
msgid "Next steps"
msgstr "下一步"

#: src/system/media.md:244
msgid "[Audio Capture](audio.md) — Microphone input + dB metering"
msgstr "[Audio Capture](audio.md) —— 麦克风输入 + 分贝测量"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:3
msgid ""
"Two `perry/system` capabilities that wrap the OS's location and photo-"
"library pickers across iOS, Android, macOS, and stub on every other "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"两个 `perry/system` 能力，封装了 iOS、Android、macOS 上的操作系统位置和照片库选择器，在所有其他平台上为桩。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:7
msgid "Geolocation"
msgstr "地理定位"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:9
msgid ""
"Callback-based; wrap in `new Promise(r => …)` at the call site if a Promise-"
"shaped API is preferred."
msgstr "基于回调；如果偏好 Promise 形式的 API，可以在调用处用 `new Promise(r => …)` 包装。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:12
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import {\n"
"  geolocationGetCurrent,\n"
"  geolocationWatch,\n"
"  geolocationStopWatch,\n"
"  geolocationRequestPermission,\n"
"} from \"perry/system\";\n"
"\n"
"geolocationGetCurrent(\n"
"  (lat, lng, accuracy, timestampMs) => {\n"
"    console.log(`at ${lat},${lng} ±${accuracy}m`);\n"
"  },\n"
"  (errorMessage) => {\n"
"    console.error(\"location failed:\", errorMessage);\n"
"  },\n"
");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/system/geolocation.md:30
msgid "`geolocationGetCurrent(onSuccess, onError)`"
msgstr "`geolocationGetCurrent(onSuccess, onError)`"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:32
msgid ""
"Resolve the device's current position. Exactly one of the two callbacks "
"fires per invocation:"
msgstr "解析设备的当前位置。每次调用恰好触发两个回调中的一个："

#: src/system/geolocation.md:35
msgid ""
"`onSuccess(lat, lng, accuracy, timestampMs)` — `accuracy` in meters "
"(horizontal); `timestampMs` is Unix epoch milliseconds."
msgstr ""
"`onSuccess(lat, lng, accuracy, timestampMs)` —— `accuracy` "
"单位为米（水平方向）；`timestampMs` 为 Unix 时间戳毫秒数。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:37
msgid ""
"`onError(message)` — fires on permission denial, timeout, or platform "
"unavailability. Common messages: `\"permission-denied\"`, `\"no-location\"`,"
" `\"no-provider-available\"`, `\"unsupported-platform\"`."
msgstr ""
"`onError(message)` —— 在权限拒绝、超时或平台不可用时触发。常见消息：`\"permission-denied\"`、`\"no-"
"location\"`、`\"no-provider-available\"`、`\"unsupported-platform\"`。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:42
msgid "`geolocationWatch(callback): number`"
msgstr "`geolocationWatch(callback): number`"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:44
msgid ""
"Subscribe to position updates. Returns a numeric watch id; pass it to "
"`geolocationStopWatch` to cancel. Updates fire whenever the platform reports"
" movement greater than the OS's default distance filter."
msgstr ""
"订阅位置更新。返回数字型 watch id；将其传给 `geolocationStopWatch` "
"以取消。每当平台报告超过操作系统默认距离过滤器的移动时触发更新。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:48
msgid "`geolocationStopWatch(id)`"
msgstr "`geolocationStopWatch(id)`"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:50
msgid "Cancel a watch started by `geolocationWatch`. No-op on unknown ids."
msgstr "取消由 `geolocationWatch` 启动的监视。对未知 id 为空操作。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:52
msgid "`geolocationRequestPermission(callback)`"
msgstr "`geolocationRequestPermission(callback)`"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:54
msgid ""
"Request location permission. Calls `callback(status)` where status is one of"
" `\"granted\"`, `\"denied\"`, `\"restricted\"`, or `\"unsupported-"
"platform\"`. Safe to call repeatedly — already-granted permissions return "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"请求位置权限。调用 `callback(status)`，其中 status 为 "
"`\"granted\"`、`\"denied\"`、`\"restricted\"` 或 `\"unsupported-platform\"` "
"之一。可重复调用 —— 已授予的权限会立即返回。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:59
msgid "Required configuration"
msgstr "必需配置"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:63 src/system/geolocation.md:127
#: src/system/background.md:80
msgid "**iOS**"
msgstr "**iOS**"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:63
msgid ""
"`NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription` in `Info.plist`. Backed by "
"`CLLocationManager`."
msgstr ""
"`Info.plist` 中需要 `NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription`。底层使用 "
"`CLLocationManager`。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:64
msgid ""
"`<uses-permission "
"android:name=\"android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION\"/>` (or "
"`ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION`) in `AndroidManifest.xml`. Backed by "
"`LocationManager`."
msgstr ""
"`AndroidManifest.xml` 中需要 `<uses-permission "
"android:name=\"android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION\"/>`（或 "
"`ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION`）。底层使用 `LocationManager`。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:65
msgid ""
"`NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription` in `Info.plist` for sandboxed apps. "
"Backed by `CLLocationManager`."
msgstr ""
"对于沙盒应用，`Info.plist` 中需要 `NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription`。底层使用 "
"`CLLocationManager`。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:66
msgid "**tvOS / watchOS / visionOS / GTK4 / Windows / Web**"
msgstr "**tvOS / watchOS / visionOS / GTK4 / Windows / Web**"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:66
msgid ""
"No-op stub — `geolocationGetCurrent` invokes `onError` immediately with "
"`\"unsupported-platform\"`."
msgstr ""
"空操作桩 —— `geolocationGetCurrent` 立即用 `\"unsupported-platform\"` 触发 `onError`。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:68
msgid "Promise wrapper"
msgstr "Promise 包装器"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:70
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { geolocationGetCurrent } from \"perry/system\";\n"
"\n"
"function getPosition(): Promise<{\n"
"  lat: number;\n"
"  lng: number;\n"
"  accuracy: number;\n"
"  timestamp: number;\n"
"}> {\n"
"  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n"
"    geolocationGetCurrent(\n"
"      (lat, lng, accuracy, timestamp) =>\n"
"        resolve({ lat, lng, accuracy, timestamp }),\n"
"      (msg) => reject(new Error(msg)),\n"
"    );\n"
"  });\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/system/geolocation.md:89
msgid "Image picker"
msgstr "图像选择器"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:91
msgid ""
"Present the native photo-library picker. The callback receives an array of "
"absolute filesystem paths the user selected; read bytes via "
"`fs.readFileSync(path)` if needed."
msgstr "呈现原生照片库选择器。回调接收用户选择的绝对文件系统路径数组；如有需要，可通过 `fs.readFileSync(path)` 读取字节。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:95
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { imagePickerPick } from \"perry/system\";\n"
"\n"
"imagePickerPick(\n"
"  5,        // maxCount\n"
"  true,     // allowMultiple\n"
"  (paths) => {\n"
"    if (paths.length === 0) {\n"
"      console.log(\"user cancelled\");\n"
"    } else {\n"
"      for (const p of paths) {\n"
"        console.log(\"picked:\", p);\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  },\n"
");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/system/geolocation.md:113
msgid "`imagePickerPick(maxCount, allowMultiple, callback)`"
msgstr "`imagePickerPick(maxCount, allowMultiple, callback)`"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:115
msgid ""
"`maxCount: number` — soft cap on selections. iOS Photo Picker enforces this "
"when API supports; Android Photo Picker (API 33+) accepts a max in `[1, "
"10]`."
msgstr ""
"`maxCount: number` —— 选择数量软上限。当 API 支持时，iOS 照片选择器会强制执行该限制；Android 照片选择器（API "
"33+）接受 `[1, 10]` 范围内的最大值。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:118
msgid ""
"`allowMultiple: boolean` — if `false`, only one image can be picked "
"regardless of `maxCount`."
msgstr "`allowMultiple: boolean` —— 若为 `false`，无论 `maxCount` 如何，都只能选择一张图像。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:120
msgid ""
"`callback(paths: string[])` — fires once when the user dismisses the picker."
" `paths` is empty if the user cancelled."
msgstr "`callback(paths: string[])` —— 在用户关闭选择器时触发一次。如果用户取消，`paths` 为空。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:127
msgid "`PHPickerViewController`"
msgstr "`PHPickerViewController`"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:127
msgid "None — the system picker doesn't require Photos permission"
msgstr "无 —— 系统选择器不需要 Photos 权限"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:128
msgid "**Android (API 33+)**"
msgstr "**Android (API 33+)**"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:128
msgid "`MediaStore.ACTION_PICK_IMAGES` (Photo Picker)"
msgstr "`MediaStore.ACTION_PICK_IMAGES`（照片选择器）"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:128
msgid "None — privacy-preserving"
msgstr "无 —— 保护隐私"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:129
msgid "**Android (API \\< 33)**"
msgstr "**Android (API \\< 33)**"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:129
msgid "`ACTION_GET_CONTENT` fallback"
msgstr "`ACTION_GET_CONTENT` 后备方案"

