#: src/testing/geisterhand.md:111
msgid ""
"```\n"
"POST /click/:handle\n"
"→ {\"ok\":true}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/testing/geisterhand.md:116
msgid ""
"Fires the widget's `onClick` callback. Works with buttons, menu items, "
"shortcuts, and table rows."
msgstr "触发该控件的 `onClick` 回调。适用于按钮、菜单项、快捷键和表格行。"

