"Benchmarks on Apple Silicon (M-series, ARM64), `min` of 3 runs each, LLVM "
"19, perry 0.5.569. Run `scripts/perf_bench.sh` to reproduce."
msgstr ""
"在 Apple Silicon（M 系列、ARM64）上的基准测试，每项取 3 次运行的 `min`，LLVM 19，perry 0.5.569。运行 "
"`scripts/perf_bench.sh` 复现。"

#: src/cli/fast-math.md:108
msgid "Benchmark"
msgstr "基准测试"

#: src/cli/fast-math.md:108
msgid "Ratio"
msgstr "比例"

#: src/cli/fast-math.md:108
