msgid ""
"The wider supply-chain hardening series "
"([`#495`–`#506`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues?q=is%3Aissue+label%3Aenhancement+security))."
msgstr ""
"更广泛的供应链加固系列（[`#495`–`#506`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues?q=is%3Aissue+label%3Aenhancement+security)）。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:3
msgid ""
"Wraps `cargo build` invocations triggered by `perry.nativeLibrary` "
"resolution in macOS `sandbox-exec`, so `build.rs` scripts shipped by third-"
"party crates can't reach the network or write outside the build output "
"directory. Build-time only — **zero runtime cost** in the produced binary. "
"(#505)"
msgstr ""
"将由 `perry.nativeLibrary` 解析触发的 `cargo build` 调用包裹在 macOS `sandbox-exec` "
"中，使第三方 crate 附带的 `build.rs` "
"脚本无法访问网络或向构建输出目录以外的位置写入文件。仅在构建时生效——对生成的二进制文件**零运行时开销**。(#505)"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:9 src/cli/emit-attest.md:10
#: src/cli/capabilities.md:15
msgid "Why"
msgstr "原因"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:11
msgid ""
"`perry.nativeLibrary` resolution kicks off `cargo build` for any source-"
"distributed crate. A crate's `build.rs` runs with full developer privileges,"
" so a typical `bun add @vendor/native-thing` silently grants the new "
"dependency the ability to exfiltrate environment variables, read SSH keys, "
"or modify files outside the build tree. The flag flips that to _opt-out_ via"
" an explicit allow-list rather than _opt-in_ via review."
msgstr ""
"`perry.nativeLibrary` 解析会为任何以源码分发的 crate 启动 `cargo build`。crate 的 `build.rs`"
" 以完整的开发者权限运行，因此典型的 `bun add @vendor/native-thing` 会悄无声息地授予新依赖窃取环境变量、读取 SSH "
"密钥或修改构建树以外文件的能力。该标志将此行为从_选择加入审查_翻转为通过显式允许列表_选择退出_。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:19
msgid "Opt-in"
msgstr "启用方式"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:21
msgid ""
"Off by default for backwards compatibility. Enable per build via env var:"
msgstr "为保持向后兼容，默认关闭。通过环境变量在每次构建时启用："

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:28
msgid ""
"CI typically sets the env var on every job; local development keeps the "
"legacy flow until ready."
msgstr "CI 通常在每个任务中设置该环境变量；本地开发在准备就绪前保持旧有流程。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:31
msgid "Profile contents"
msgstr "Profile 内容"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:33
msgid "The generated `sandbox-exec` profile:"
msgstr "生成的 `sandbox-exec` profile："

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:35
msgid "`deny default` + `deny network*` — `build.rs` cannot phone home."
msgstr "`deny default` + `deny network*` — `build.rs` 无法进行网络回调。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:36
msgid ""
"`allow file-read*` everywhere (cargo / rustc need to read system libraries, "
"source, dependency crates)."
msgstr "`allow file-read*` 全局开放（cargo / rustc 需要读取系统库、源码和依赖 crate）。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:38
msgid ""
"`allow file-write*` scoped to `target/`, `~/.cargo`, `~/.rustup`, `/tmp`, "
"and the per-build `TempDir`."
msgstr ""
"`allow file-write*` 的作用范围限定于 `target/`、`~/.cargo`、`~/.rustup`、`/tmp` 以及每次构建的"
" `TempDir`。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:40
msgid ""
"`allow process-fork` + `process-exec` so rustc, cc, ld, and the build.rs "
"binaries themselves can run."
msgstr ""
"`allow process-fork` + `process-exec`，以便 rustc、cc、ld 以及 build.rs "
"生成的二进制文件本身可以运行。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:42
msgid ""
"`allow sysctl-read` / `mach-lookup` / `iokit-open` for the platform queries "
"cargo and rustc routinely issue."
msgstr ""
"`allow sysctl-read` / `mach-lookup` / `iokit-open`，用于 cargo 和 rustc "
"例行发起的平台查询。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:45
msgid "Pre-fetch workflow"
msgstr "预拉取工作流"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:47
msgid ""
"The sandbox denies network, so cargo cannot reach `crates.io` from inside "
"it. Pre-fetch once outside the sandbox before the sandboxed build:"
msgstr "沙箱会拒绝网络访问，因此 cargo 无法在沙箱内部访问 `crates.io`。在沙箱化构建之前，请在沙箱外先执行一次预拉取："

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:56
msgid ""
"CI runners typically cache `~/.cargo` across jobs, so the pre-fetch is free "
"on subsequent builds."
msgstr "CI 运行器通常会在作业之间缓存 `~/.cargo`，因此后续构建的预拉取开销为零。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:59
msgid "Per-package escape hatch"
msgstr "按包配置的豁免机制"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:61
msgid ""
"Some legitimate crates need network during `build.rs` (e.g. fetching "
"prebuilt artifacts from a CDN). Opt them out per-package in the **host** "
"`package.json`:"
msgstr ""
"某些合法的 crate 在 `build.rs` 期间需要访问网络（例如从 CDN 获取预构建产物）。可在**宿主** `package.json` "
"中按包进行豁免："

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:68
msgid "\"allowUnsandboxedBuild\""
msgstr ""

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:68
msgid "\"@some-vendor/builds-with-network\""
msgstr ""

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:73
msgid ""
"Host-controlled — transitive deps cannot opt themselves out. The exemption "
"lives in the host repository's `package.json` and shows up in code review."
msgstr "由宿主控制——传递依赖无法自行申请豁免。豁免配置位于宿主仓库的 `package.json` 中，并会出现在代码审查中。"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:77
msgid "Cross-platform scope"
msgstr "跨平台支持范围"

#: src/cli/sandbox-buildrs.md:79
msgid ""
"MVP is macOS-only (the `sandbox-exec` profile). Linux landlock support is "
"tracked separately; until that lands, `PERRY_SANDBOX_BUILDRS=1` on Linux is "
"a no-op (the build runs normally). Windows: out of scope."
msgstr ""
"MVP 仅支持 macOS（`sandbox-exec` 配置文件）。Linux landlock 支持单独追踪；在该功能落地之前，Linux 上的 "
"`PERRY_SANDBOX_BUILDRS=1` 为空操作（构建正常运行）。Windows：不在支持范围内。"

