msgstr "已链接 `perry-jsruntime`"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:47
msgid "Allow `dynamic-code-generation` (QuickJS JIT)"
msgstr "允许 `dynamic-code-generation`（QuickJS JIT）"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:48
msgid "Always"
msgstr "始终"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:48
msgid ""
"Deny default. Allow `file-read*` on system locations + `/dev/null` + "
"`/dev/urandom` so the dynamic linker reaches `main()`."
msgstr ""
"默认拒绝。允许 `file-read*` 作用于系统路径 + `/dev/null` + `/dev/urandom`，以便动态链接器能够到达 "
"`main()`。"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:50
msgid ""
"The generated profile is a _starting point_ — review and tighten manually "
"for production builds. Per-API HIR-driven refinement (which would "
"distinguish `fs.readFileSync`\\-only deps from `fs.writeFileSync` deps, or "
"`fetch(\"https://api.example.com/...\")` from `fetch(url)`) lands as a "
"follow-up under the same flag."
msgstr ""
"生成的配置文件是一个 _起点_——请针对生产构建手动审查并收紧。基于 HIR 的按 API 精细化控制（可区分仅依赖 `fs.readFileSync`"
" 与依赖 `fs.writeFileSync`，或区分 `fetch(\"https://api.example.com/...\")` 与 "
"`fetch(url)`）将作为同一标志下的后续工作落地。"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:56
msgid "Header documents itself"
msgstr "头部注释自说明"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:58
msgid ""
"The emitted profile starts with a documentation header that shows the "
"`sandbox-exec -f ... ...` invocation and cites #506 for context — so "
"downstream operators can see immediately how to apply it without hunting "
"through Perry docs."
msgstr ""
"生成的配置文件以文档注释头开头，展示 `sandbox-exec -f ... ...` 的调用方式，并引用 #506 "
"提供上下文——以便下游运维人员无需查阅 Perry 文档即可立即了解如何应用该配置文件。"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:63
msgid "Composition with `--lockdown`"
msgstr "与 `--lockdown` 的组合使用"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:65
msgid ""
"When the `--lockdown` mode (#496) lands, it will default `--emit-sandbox` "
"on. For now they're orthogonal."
msgstr "当 `--lockdown` 模式（#496）落地时，它将默认启用 `--emit-sandbox`。目前两者相互独立。"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:68
msgid "What's NOT covered (MVP)"
msgstr "MVP 未涵盖的内容"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:70
msgid "Linux `seccomp` BPF filter + landlock FS scoping — follow-up."
msgstr "Linux `seccomp` BPF 过滤器 + landlock 文件系统范围限定——后续工作。"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:71
