msgstr "Windows AppContainer 清单——后续工作。"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:72
msgid ""
"Per-API HIR-driven refinement (`fs.readFileSync` ≠ `fs.writeFileSync`, "
"literal-host extraction for `fetch`)."
msgstr ""
"基于 HIR 的按 API 精细化控制（`fs.readFileSync` ≠ `fs.writeFileSync`，`fetch` "
"的字面量主机提取）。"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:74
msgid ""
"Auto-loading the profile at process start via `sandbox_init` instead of the "
"`sandbox-exec` wrapper."
msgstr "通过 `sandbox_init` 在进程启动时自动加载配置文件，替代 `sandbox-exec` 包装器。"

#: src/cli/emit-sandbox.md:76
msgid ""
"iOS / Android — already sandboxed by the platform at process launch; out of "
