#: src/contributing/architecture.md:58
msgid ""
"Generational mark-sweep GC, per-thread arena split into nursery + old-gen. "
"Roots come from a precise shadow stack (emitted by codegen), a conservative "
"native-stack scan, and 9 registered runtime scanners. Two-bit aging tenures "
"objects after surviving 2 minor cycles; a write barrier maintains a "
"remembered set for old → young pointers."
msgstr ""
"分代标记-清除 GC，每线程 arena 分为新生代（nursery）和老生代（old-gen）。根来源包括：codegen "
"生成的精确影子栈、保守的原生栈扫描，以及 9 个已注册的运行时扫描器。两位老化机制在对象存活 2 次 minor GC "
"周期后将其晋升；写屏障维护一个记录集，用于追踪老生代指向新生代的指针。"

#: src/contributing/architecture.md:60
msgid ""
"See [Internals → Memory Model](../internals/memory-model.md) for the full "
"picture (NaN-boxing, heap layout, root discovery, generational behaviour, "
"env-var escape hatches)."
msgstr ""
"完整介绍（NaN-boxing、堆布局、根发现、分代行为、环境变量逃生舱）请参阅[内部机制 → 内存模型](../internals/memory-"
"model.md)。"

